	(728,1,14,'yii2-Data widgets','&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Data widgets&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n数据小部件\r\nYii provides a set of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-widgets&quot;&gt;widgets&lt;/a&gt; that can be used to display data. \r\nYii提供一套可以用于显示数据的widget。\r\nWhile the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-widgets#detail-view&quot;&gt;DetailView&lt;/a&gt; widget can be used to display data for a single record, \r\n虽然DetailView小部件可用于显示单个记录的数据，\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-widgets#list-view&quot;&gt;ListView&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-widgets#grid-view&quot;&gt;GridView&lt;/a&gt; can be used to display a list or table of data records providing features like pagination, sorting and filtering.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-widgets#list-view&quot;&gt;ListView&lt;/a&gt; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-widgets#grid-view&quot;&gt;GridView&lt;/a&gt; 可用于显示一个数据记录的列表或表格，提供了分页，存储和筛选功能。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;DetailView\r\nThe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-detailview&quot;&gt;DetailView&lt;/a&gt; widget displays the details of a single data &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-detailview#$model-detail&quot;&gt;model&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-detailview&quot;&gt;DetailView&lt;/a&gt; widget显示单个数据model的详情。\r\nIt is best used for displaying a model in a regular format (e.g. each model attribute is displayed as a row in a table). \r\n它非常适合用常规格式显示一个模型（例如在一个表格的一行中显示模型的每个属性）。\r\nThe model can be either an instance or subclass of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Model&lt;/a&gt; such as an &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-active-record&quot;&gt;active record&lt;/a&gt; or an associative array.\r\n这里说的模型可以是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Model&lt;/a&gt; 的实例或者其子类的一个实例，例如子类 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/zh-cn/db-active-record&quot;&gt;active record&lt;/a&gt;，也可以是一个关联数组。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;DetailView uses the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-detailview#$attributes-detail&quot;&gt;$attributes&lt;/a&gt; property to determine which model attributes should be displayed and how they should be formatted. \r\nDetailView使用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-detailview#$attributes-detail&quot;&gt;$attributes&lt;/a&gt; 属性来决定显示模型哪些属性以及如何格式化它们。\r\nSee the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-formatting&quot;&gt;formatter section&lt;/a&gt; for available formatting options.\r\n可用的格式化选项，见 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/zh-cn/output-formatting&quot;&gt;formatter section&lt;/a&gt; 章节。\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;A typical usage of DetailView is as follows:\r\n一个典型DetailView 的用法如下：\r\necho DetailView::widget([\r\n    &amp;#39;model&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $model,\r\n    &amp;#39;attributes&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n        &amp;#39;title&amp;#39;,                                           // title attribute (in plain text)\r\n        &amp;#39;description:html&amp;#39;,                                // description attribute formatted as HTML\r\n        [                                                  // the owner name of the model\r\n            &amp;#39;label&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;Owner&amp;#39;,\r\n            &amp;#39;value&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $model-&amp;gt;owner-&amp;gt;name,            \r\n            &amp;#39;contentOptions&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;bg-red&amp;#39;],     // HTML attributes to customize value tag\r\n            &amp;#39;captionOptions&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;tooltip&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;Tooltip&amp;#39;],  // HTML attributes to customize label tag\r\n        ],\r\n        &amp;#39;created_at:datetime&amp;#39;,                             // creation date formatted as datetime\r\n    ],\r\n]);&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Remember that unlike yii\\widgets\\GridView which processes a set of models,\r\n记住，与处理一组模型的yii\\widgets\\GridView不同，\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-detailview&quot;&gt;DetailView&lt;/a&gt; processes just one. \r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-detailview&quot;&gt;DetailView&lt;/a&gt;只处理一个。\r\nSo most of the time there is no need for using closure \r\n所以，多数时间不需要使用闭包,\r\nsince &lt;code&gt;$model&lt;/code&gt; is the only one model for display \r\n因为 &lt;code&gt;$model&lt;/code&gt; 是唯一一个用于显示的模型，\r\nand available in view as a variable.\r\n并且可以作为一个变量在视图中使用。\r\nHowever some cases can make using of closure useful. \r\n但是，有些情况下可以使用闭包。\r\nFor example when &lt;code&gt;visible&lt;/code&gt; is specified and you want to prevent &lt;code&gt;value&lt;/code&gt; calculations in case it evaluates to &lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;:\r\n例如指定了 &lt;code&gt;visible&lt;/code&gt;，并且你不想让&lt;code&gt;value&lt;/code&gt; 的结果为 &lt;code&gt;false：&lt;/code&gt;\r\n&lt;code&gt;echo DetailView::widget([\r\n    &amp;#39;model&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $model,\r\n    &amp;#39;attributes&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n        [\r\n            &amp;#39;attribute&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;owner&amp;#39;,\r\n            &amp;#39;value&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; function ($model) {\r\n                return $model-&amp;gt;owner-&amp;gt;name;\r\n            },\r\n            &amp;#39;visible&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; \\Yii::$app-&amp;gt;user-&amp;gt;can(&amp;#39;posts.owner.view&amp;#39;),\r\n        ],\r\n    ],\r\n]);&lt;/code&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;ListView\r\nThe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-listview&quot;&gt;ListView&lt;/a&gt; widget is used to display data from a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-providers&quot;&gt;data provider&lt;/a&gt;. \r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-listview&quot;&gt;ListView&lt;/a&gt; widget 是用于显示&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-providers&quot;&gt;data provider&lt;/a&gt;数据。\r\nEach data model is rendered using the specified &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-listview#$itemView-detail&quot;&gt;view file&lt;/a&gt;. \r\n每个数据model使用指定的视图文件渲染的。\r\nSince it provides features such as pagination, sorting and filtering out of the box, \r\n因为它提供了开箱即用的一些功能如分页，排序，过滤\r\nit is handy both to display information to end user and to create data managing UI.\r\n它既可以方便地向最终用户显示信息，也可以方便地创建数据管理界面。\r\nA typical usage is as follows:\r\n典型用法如下：\r\nuse yii\\widgets\\ListView;\r\nuse yii\\data\\ActiveDataProvider;\r\n\r\n$dataProvider = new ActiveDataProvider([\r\n    &amp;#39;query&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; Post::find(),\r\n    &amp;#39;pagination&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n        &amp;#39;pageSize&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; 20,\r\n    ],\r\n]);\r\necho ListView::widget([\r\n    &amp;#39;dataProvider&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $dataProvider,\r\n    &amp;#39;itemView&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;_post&amp;#39;,\r\n]);&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;The &lt;code&gt;_post&lt;/code&gt; view file could contain the following:\r\n&lt;code&gt;_post视图文件可包含如下：&lt;/code&gt;\r\n&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;?php\r\nuse yii\\helpers\\Html;\r\nuse yii\\helpers\\HtmlPurifier;\r\n?&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;post&amp;quot;&amp;gt;\r\n    &amp;lt;h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;?= Html::encode($model-&amp;gt;title) ?&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;\r\n\r\n    &amp;lt;?= HtmlPurifier::process($model-&amp;gt;text) ?&amp;gt;    \r\n&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;In the view file above, \r\n在上面的视图中，\r\nthe current data model is available as &lt;code&gt;$model&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n当前的数据模型 &lt;code&gt;$model&lt;/code&gt; 是可用的。\r\nAdditionally the following variables are available:\r\n此外，还提供以下变量：\r\n&lt;code&gt;$key&lt;/code&gt;: mixed, the key value associated with the data item.\r\n&lt;code&gt;$key&lt;/code&gt;: 混合类型, 键的值与数据项相关联。\r\n&lt;code&gt;$index&lt;/code&gt;: integer, the zero-based index of the data item in the items array returned by the data provider.\r\n&lt;code&gt;$index&lt;/code&gt;: integer,是由数据提供者返回的数组中以0起始的数据项的索引。\r\n&lt;code&gt;$widget&lt;/code&gt;: ListView, this widget instance.\r\n&lt;code&gt;$widget&lt;/code&gt;: ListView, widget 实例。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;If you need to pass additional data to each view, \r\n假如你需要传递附加数据到每一个视图中，\r\nyou can use the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-listview#$viewParams-detail&quot;&gt;$viewParams&lt;/a&gt; property to pass key value pairs like the following:\r\n你可已使用&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-listview#$viewParams-detail&quot;&gt;$viewParams&lt;/a&gt; 属性传递键值对，如下所示：\r\n\r\necho ListView::widget([\r\n    &amp;#39;dataProvider&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $dataProvider,\r\n    &amp;#39;itemView&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;_post&amp;#39;,\r\n    &amp;#39;viewParams&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n        &amp;#39;fullView&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; true,\r\n        &amp;#39;context&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;main-page&amp;#39;,\r\n        // ...\r\n    ],\r\n]);&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;These are then also available as variables in the view.\r\n这些也可以作为视图中的变量使用。\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;GridView&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nData grid or &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-gridview&quot;&gt;GridView&lt;/a&gt; is one of the most powerful Yii widgets. \r\n数据网格或网格视图是Yii widget 更强大的其中之一\r\nIt is extremely useful if you need to quickly build the admin section of the system. \r\n如果你需要快速建立系统的管理后台， GridView 非常有用。\r\nIt takes data from a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-data-providers&quot;&gt;data provider&lt;/a&gt; and renders each row using a set of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-gridview#$columns-detail&quot;&gt;columns&lt;/a&gt; presenting data in the form of a table.\r\n它从数据提供者 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/zh-cn/output-data-providers&quot;&gt;data provider&lt;/a&gt; 中取得数据并使用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-gridview#$columns-detail&quot;&gt;columns&lt;/a&gt; 属性的一组列配置，在一个表格中渲染每一行数据。\r\n\r\nEach row of the table represents the data of a single data item, \r\n表中的每一行代表一个数据项的数据，\r\nand a column usually represents an attribute of the item (some columns may correspond to complex expressions of attributes or static text).\r\n并且一列通常表示该项的属性 （某些列可以对应于属性或静态文本的复杂表达式）。\r\n\r\nThe minimal code needed to use GridView is as follows:\r\n使用GridView的最少代码如下：\r\nuse yii\\grid\\GridView;\r\nuse yii\\data\\ActiveDataProvider;\r\n\r\n$dataProvider = new ActiveDataProvider([\r\n    &amp;#39;query&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; Post::find(),\r\n    &amp;#39;pagination&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n        &amp;#39;pageSize&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; 20,\r\n    ],\r\n]);\r\necho GridView::widget([\r\n    &amp;#39;dataProvider&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $dataProvider,\r\n]);&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write preformatted text…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;The above code first creates a data provider \r\n上面的代码首先创建了一个data provider\r\nand then uses GridView to display every attribute in every row taken from the data provider. \r\n然后使用GridView显示每一行的每个属性，每一行的数据是从数据提供者取来的。\r\nThe displayed table is equipped with sorting and pagination functionality out of the box.\r\n展现出来的表格封装了排序以及分页功能。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Grid columns&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n网格列\r\nThe columns of the grid table are configured in terms of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-column&quot;&gt;yii\\grid\\Column&lt;/a&gt; classes, \r\n表格的列是通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-column&quot;&gt;yii\\grid\\Column&lt;/a&gt; 类来配置的\r\nwhich are configured in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-gridview#$columns-detail&quot;&gt;columns&lt;/a&gt; property of GridView configuration. \r\n该类是通过 GridView 配置项中的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-gridview#$columns-detail&quot;&gt;columns&lt;/a&gt; 属性配置的。\r\nDepending on column type and settings these are able to present data differently. \r\n根据列类型和设置，它们能够以不同的方式显示数据。\r\nThe default class is &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-datacolumn&quot;&gt;yii\\grid\\DataColumn&lt;/a&gt;, \r\n默认的类是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-datacolumn&quot;&gt;yii\\grid\\DataColumn&lt;/a&gt;，\r\nwhich represents a model attribute and can be sorted and filtered by.\r\n它表示一个模型属性，可以根据它进行排序和筛选。\r\necho GridView::widget([\r\n    &amp;#39;dataProvider&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $dataProvider,\r\n    &amp;#39;columns&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n        [&amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;yii\\grid\\SerialColumn&amp;#39;],\r\n        // Simple columns defined by the data contained in $dataProvider.\r\n        // Data from the model&amp;#39;s column will be used.\r\n        &amp;#39;id&amp;#39;,\r\n        &amp;#39;username&amp;#39;,\r\n        // More complex one.\r\n        [\r\n            &amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;yii\\grid\\DataColumn&amp;#39;, // can be omitted, as it is the default\r\n            &amp;#39;value&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; function ($data) {\r\n                return $data-&amp;gt;name; // $data[&amp;#39;name&amp;#39;] for array data, e.g. using SqlDataProvider.\r\n            },\r\n        ],\r\n    ],\r\n]);\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Note that if the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-gridview#$columns-detail&quot;&gt;columns&lt;/a&gt; part of the configuration isn&amp;#39;t specified,\r\n请注意，假如配置中没有指定 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-grid-gridview#$columns-detail&quot;&gt;columns&lt;/a&gt; 属性， \r\nYii tries to show all possible columns of the data provider&amp;#39;s model.\r\nYii 会试图显示数据提供者的模型中所有可能的列。\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Column classes&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n列类\r\nGrid columns could be customized by using different column classes:\r\n可以使用不同的列类自定义网格列：\r\necho GridView::widget([\r\n    &amp;#39;dataProvider&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $dataProvider,\r\n    &amp;#39;columns&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n        [\r\n            &amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;yii\\grid\\SerialColumn&amp;#39;, // &amp;lt;-- here\r\n            // you may configure additional properties here\r\n        ],&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Powered by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1&quot; title=&quot;Froala Editor&quot;&gt;Froala Editor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','2018-03-28 16:05:08','2020-03-07 23:31:59','1'),
	(729,1,81,'docker','&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;从开发环境到生产环境&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nDocker最好的使用方式是将应用程序代码预先打包成一个Docker镜像。\r\n镜像通常包含所有的应用程序代码、运行时的依赖以及系统的需求。\r\n而包含数据库凭证和其他敏感信息的配置文件通常在运行时添加，\r\n而非内建到镜像中。\r\n\r\n有些团队会在开发机上手工构建Docker镜像，\r\n然后推送到镜像仓库，之后再从仓库中拉取镜像到生产环境宿主机中。\r\n这是个很简单的用例。虽然行得通，但从工作流和安全角度考虑并不理想。\r\n\r\n一个更常见的生产环境示例是，\r\n使用持续集成/持续交付系统在应用程序代码或Dockerfile文件发生变更时自动构建新镜像。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;使用Docker的多种方式&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n将应用的后台程序迁移到Docker集群中，\r\n同时保持网页服务器和数据库服务器不变是开始使用Docker的常见示例。\r\n另一示例是将应用的部分REST API迁移到Docker中运行，\r\n前端使用Nginx代理在遗留服务和Docker集群之间路由通信。\r\n通过使用此类技术，团队可以渐进式地从单体应用无缝地迁移到面向服务架构。\r\n如今的应用程序往往需要几十个第三方库，\r\n用于加速功能开发或连接第三方SaaS和数据库服务。每个库都可能产生bug，\r\n或是让用户陷入版本依赖的泥沼。再加上库的频繁更改，\r\n要在基础设施上完成工作代码的持续部署而不引起失败，压力巨大。\r\n\r\nDocker可贵的镜像思想使得技术团队在部署工作代码时，\r\n不论是单体架构、面向服务或是二者的混合，\r\n由于代码及其依赖项捆绑在同一个镜像中，\r\n所使用的方式对每次部署都是可测试、可重复、文档化且一致的。\r\n一旦一个镜像构建完毕，就可以部署到任意多个运行着Docker守护进程的服务器上。\r\n另外一个常见的Docker用例是跨环境部署一个单一容器，\r\n其典型的代码路径是从开发环境到预演环境再到生产环境。\r\n容器为整个代码路径提供了一个一致的、可测试的环境。\r\n\r\n作为一个开发人员，Docker模型允许在其个人电脑上调试与生产环境完全一致的代码。\r\n开发人员可以很容易地下载、运行和调试有问题的生产环境镜像，且无需事先对本地开发环境进行修改。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;可预期的情况\r\n&lt;/strong&gt;在生产环境中运行Docker容器困难不小，但还是能实现的。\r\n每天都有越来越多公司开始在生产环境中运行Docker。\r\n如同所有的基础设施一样，我们建议以小规模入手，然后渐进式地完成迁移。\r\n&lt;strong&gt;为什么Docker在生产环境如此困难&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n对生产环境有很多要求：\r\n安全可靠的部署、健康检查、最小或零停机时间、从失败中恢复的能力（回滚）、一个集中存储日志的方式、一种分析或调试应用的方式，\r\n以及一种聚合监控参数的方式。类似Docker这样的新技术虽然使用起来非常有趣，但还需要时间来完善。\r\nDocker在可移植性、一致性以及打包具有众多依赖的服务这些方面非常有优势。多数团队会因为以下一个或多个痛点而坚持使用Docker。\r\n一个应用的不同部分使用大量不同的依赖。\r\n支持使用旧依赖的遗留应用程序。\r\n开发团队与DevOps之间的工作流问题。\r\n本书中我们所采访的团队，有一个共同的警示：\r\n切勿尝试在一个组织内让采用Docker这事一蹴而就。\r\n即便运维团队已经为采用Docker做好了充分的准备，也请记住，\r\n过渡到Docker通常意味着将管理依赖的重任推给了开发人员。\r\n虽然很多开发人员都渴求这种自主权，以便加快迭代，\r\n但并非每位开发人员都有能力或兴趣将其列入自己的责任范围。\r\n为了能有一个良好的Docker工作流，\r\n还是需要花些时间来转变企业文化。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Powered by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1&quot; title=&quot;Froala Editor&quot;&gt;Froala Editor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','2018-03-28 16:05:08','2020-02-28 19:05:24','1'),
	(730,1,14,'the document of yii2','&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is Yii  &lt;/strong&gt;\r\nyii是什么?\r\nYii is a high performance, \r\nyii是一个高性能,\r\ncomponent-based PHP framework for rapidly developing modern Web applications. \r\n基于组件快速发展的现代web应用的php框架\r\nThe name Yii (pronounced &lt;code&gt;Yee&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;[ji:]&lt;/code&gt;) means &amp;quot;simple and evolutionary&amp;quot; in Chinese. \r\nIt can also be thought of as an acronym for &lt;strong&gt;Yes It Is&lt;/strong&gt;!\r\n译文：\r\n   \r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is Yii Best for?&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nyii最适合做什么？\r\nYii is a generic Web programming framework, \r\nyii是一个通用的web程序框架，\r\nmeaning that it can be used for developing all kinds of Web applications using PHP. \r\n即可以用于开发各种用PHP构建的web应用。\r\nBecause of its component-based architecture and sophisticated caching support, \r\n因为它基于组件的结构和灵巧的缓存支持，\r\nit is especially suitable for developing large-scale applications such as portals, \r\n它特别适合开发大型应用，如如门户网站、\r\nforums, content management systems (CMS), e-commerce projects, RESTful Web services, and so on.\r\n论坛、内容管理系统（CMS）电子商务项目和 RESTful Web 服务等。\r\n译文：\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How does Yii Compare with Other Frameworks?&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nYii与其他框架相比如何？\r\nIf you&amp;#39;re already familiar with another framework, \r\n如你之前熟悉了别的框架，\r\nyou may appreciate knowing how Yii compares:\r\n你就会重视yii是如何作对比\r\nLike most PHP frameworks, \r\n像大多数框架一样，\r\nYii implements the MVC (Model-View-Controller) architectural pattern and promotes code organization based on that pattern.\r\nyii实现了MVC (Model-View-Controller)架构模式并基于该模式提升代码组织\r\nYii takes the philosophy that code should be written in a simple yet elegant way. \r\n代码应该是简洁而优雅的书写方式，这是yii的编程哲学\r\nYii will never try to over-design things mainly for the purpose of strictly following some design pattern.\r\nYii绝不会为了严格遵循某些设计模式而过度设计东西。\r\nYii is a full-stack framework providing many proven and ready-to-use features: query builders and ActiveRecord for both relational and NoSQL databases; RESTful API development support; multi-tier caching support; and more.\r\nyii 是一个全栈框架提供许多经验证且随时可用的功能:对关系型和 NoSQL 数据库都提供了查询生成器和 ActiveRecord，支持RESTful API开发，支持多层缓存还有更多\r\nYii is extremely extensible. You can customize or replace nearly every piece of the core&amp;#39;s code. \r\nyii非常容易扩展。你可以自定义或替换几乎任何一处核心代码\r\nYou can also take advantage of Yii&amp;#39;s solid extension architecture to use or develop redistributable extensions.\r\n您还可以利用Yii的可靠扩展架构来使用再开发或再发布扩展。？\r\nHigh performance is always a primary goal of Yii.\r\n高性能始终是Yii的首要目标\r\nYii is not a one-man show, \r\nYii 不是一个人在开发，\r\nit is backed up by a &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.yiiframework.com/team/&quot;&gt;strong core developer team&lt;/a&gt;, \r\n它的背后是由一个强大的核心团队\r\nas well as a large community of professionals constantly contributing to Yii&amp;#39;s development. \r\n还有一个庞大的专家社区持续不断的对Yii的开发作出贡献。\r\nThe Yii developer team keeps a close eye on the latest Web development trends and on the best practices and features found in other frameworks and projects. \r\nYii开发团队密切关注最新的Web开发趋势以及其他框架和项目中的最佳实践和特性。\r\nThe most relevant best practices and features found elsewhere are regularly incorporated into the core framework and exposed via simple and elegant interfaces.\r\n在其他地方找到的最相关的最佳实践和特性定期被纳入核心框架，并通过简单而优雅的接口公开。\r\n译文：xx\r\n   &lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yii Versions&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nyii版本\r\nYii currently has two major versions available: 1.1 and 2.0. \r\nyii当前有两个主要的版本 1.1 和 2.0\r\nVersion 1.1 is the old generation and is now in maintenance mode.\r\n1.1版本是老版本，现在是处于维护状态\r\nVersion 2.0 is a complete rewrite of Yii, \r\n2.0是一个完全重写的版本\r\nadopting the latest technologies and protocols, \r\n采用了最新的技术和协议\r\nincluding Composer, PSR, namespaces, traits, and so forth. \r\n包括依赖包管理器 Composer、PHP 代码规范 PSR、命名空间、Traits（特质）等等。\r\nVersion 2.0 represents the current generation of the framework and will receive the main development efforts over the next few years. \r\n2.0 版代表新一代框架，是未来几年中我们的主要开发版本。 \r\nThis guide is mainly about version 2.0.\r\n本指南主要基于 2.0 版编写。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements and Prerequisites&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n要求和预备知识\r\nYii 2.0 requires PHP 5.4.0 or above and runs best with the latest version of PHP 7. \r\nyii2.0要求php5.4.0 或者更高的版本运行，php7的版本运行为最好。\r\nYou can find more detailed requirements for individual features by running the requirement checker included in every Yii release.\r\n通过运行每个Yii版本中包含的需求检查器，您可以找到各个特性的更详细的需求。\r\nUsing Yii requires basic knowledge of object-oriented programming (OOP), \r\n使用Yii需要基本的面向对象编程（OOP）知识，\r\nas Yii is a pure OOP-based framework.\r\n因为Yii是一个纯面向对象的框架。\r\n Yii 2.0 also makes use of the latest features of PHP, \r\nYii 2.0还利用了PHP的最新特性，\r\nsuch as &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.namespaces.php&quot;&gt;namespaces&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.oop5.traits.php&quot;&gt;traits&lt;/a&gt;. Understanding these concepts will help you more easily pick up Yii 2.0.\r\n例如&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.namespaces.php&quot;&gt;命名空间&lt;/a&gt; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.oop5.traits.php&quot;&gt;Trait（特质）&lt;/a&gt;。 理解这些概念将有助于你更快地掌握 Yii 2.0。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upgrading from Version 1.1&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n从1.1版本升级\r\nThere are many differences between versions 1.1 and 2.0 of Yii as the framework was completely rewritten for 2.0. \r\nYii的1.1版和2.0版之间有很多不同之处，2.0 版框架是完全重写的。\r\nAs a result, upgrading from version 1.1 is not as trivial as upgrading between minor versions. \r\n 因此从 1.1 版升级并不像小版本间的跨越那么简单，\r\nIn this guide you&amp;#39;ll find the major differences between the two versions.\r\n通过本指南你将会了解两个版本间主要的不同之处\r\n在本指南中，您将发现这两个版本之间的主要区别。\r\nIf you have not used Yii 1.1 before, you can safely skip this section and turn directly to &amp;quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/start-installation&quot;&gt;Getting started&lt;/a&gt;&amp;quot;.\r\n如果您以前没有使用过yi1.1，您可以安全地跳过本节，直接转到&amp;ldquo;入门&amp;rdquo;。\r\nPlease note that Yii 2.0 introduces more new features than are covered in this summary. \r\n请注意，Yii 2.0引入的新功能比本摘要中的更多。\r\nIt is highly recommended that you read through the whole definitive guide to learn about them all. \r\n强烈建议您通读完整的权威指南，了解所有这些内容。\r\nChances are that some features you previously had to develop for yourself are now part of the core code.\r\n很有可能以前必须为自己开发的一些功能现在已经成为核心代码的一部分。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Installation&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n安装\r\nYii 2.0 fully embraces &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/&quot;&gt;Composer&lt;/a&gt;, \r\nYii 2.0 完全拥抱 &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/&quot;&gt;Composer&lt;/a&gt;，\r\nthe de facto PHP package manager. \r\n它是事实上的 PHP 依赖管理工具。\r\nInstallation of the core framework, as well as extensions, are handled through Composer. \r\n核心框架以及扩展的安装都通过 Composer 来处理。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/start-installation&quot;&gt;Installing Yii&lt;/a&gt; section to learn how to install Yii 2.0. \r\n请参阅安装Yii部分以了解如何安装Yii 2.0。\r\nIf you want to create new extensions, or turn your existing 1.1 extensions into 2.0-compatible extensions, \r\n如果你想创建新扩展，或将现有的1.1扩展转换为与2.0兼容的扩展，\r\nplease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-extensions#creating-extensions&quot;&gt;Creating Extensions&lt;/a&gt; section of the guide.\r\n你可以参考 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/zh-cn/structure-extensions#creating-extensions&quot;&gt;创建扩展&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PHP Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nPHP要求\r\nYii 2.0 requires PHP 5.4 or above, which is a huge improvement over PHP version 5.2 that is required by Yii 1.1. \r\nyii 2.0 要求 PHP 5.4或者更高，\r\nYii 2.0需要PHP 5.4或更高版本，这是对Yii 1.1所需php5.2版本的巨大改进。\r\nAs a result, there are many differences on the language level that you should pay attention to.  \r\n因此，在语言层面上有许多差异，你应该注意。\r\nBelow is a summary of the major changes regarding PHP:\r\n以下是有关PHP的主要更改摘要：\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.namespaces.php&quot;&gt;Namespaces&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/functions.anonymous.php&quot;&gt;Anonymous functions&lt;/a&gt;.\r\nShort array syntax &lt;code&gt;[...elements...]&lt;/code&gt; is used instead of &lt;code&gt;array(...elements...)&lt;/code&gt;.\r\n使用短数组语法[...elements...] 而不是 array(...elements...)。\r\nShort echo tags &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;?=&lt;/code&gt; are used in view files. This is safe to use starting from PHP 5.4.\r\n视图文件中的短格式 echo 标签 &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;?=。&lt;/code&gt;从PHP 5.4开始使用是安全的。\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/book.spl.php&quot;&gt;SPL classes and interfaces&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.oop5.late-static-bindings.php&quot;&gt;Late Static Bindings&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/zh/language.oop5.late-static-bindings.php&quot;&gt;延迟静态绑定&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/book.datetime.php&quot;&gt;Date and Time&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.oop5.traits.php&quot;&gt;Traits&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/book.intl.php&quot;&gt;intl&lt;/a&gt;. \r\nYii 2.0 makes use of the &lt;code&gt;intl&lt;/code&gt; PHP extension to support internationalization features.\r\nYii 2.0使用intl PHP扩展来支持国际化特性。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Namespace&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n命名空间\r\nThe most obvious change in Yii 2.0 is the use of namespaces. \r\nYii 2.0中最明显的变化是名称空间的使用。\r\nAlmost every core class is namespaced, e.g., &lt;code&gt;yii\\web\\Request&lt;/code&gt;.\r\n 几乎每一个核心类都引入了命名空间， 比如 &lt;code&gt;yii\\web\\Request&lt;/code&gt;。\r\nThe &amp;quot;C&amp;quot; prefix is no longer used in class names. \r\n&amp;ldquo;C&amp;rdquo;前缀不再用于类名中。\r\nThe naming scheme now follows the directory structure. \r\n命名方案现在遵循目录结构。\r\nFor example, &lt;code&gt;yii\\web\\Request&lt;/code&gt; indicates that the corresponding class file is &lt;code&gt;web/Request.php&lt;/code&gt; under the Yii framework folder.\r\n例如，yii\\web\\Request表示对应的类文件是yii framework文件夹下的web/Request.php。\r\n(You can use any core class without explicitly including that class file, thanks to the Yii class loader.)\r\n（感谢Yii类加载器，您可以使用任何核心类而不显式地包含该类文件。）&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Component and Object&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n组件与对象\r\nYii 2.0 breaks the &lt;code&gt;CComponent&lt;/code&gt; class in 1.1 into two classes: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\BaseObject&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-component&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Component&lt;/a&gt;. \r\nYii 2.0将1.1中的CComponent类分为两个类：Yii\\base\\BaseObject和Yii\\base\\Component。\r\nThe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject&quot;&gt;BaseObject&lt;/a&gt; class is a lightweight base class that allows defining &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/concept-properties&quot;&gt;object properties&lt;/a&gt; via getters and setters. \r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject&quot;&gt;BaseObject&lt;/a&gt; 类是一个轻量级基类，允许通过getter和setter定义对象属性。\r\nThe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-component&quot;&gt;Component&lt;/a&gt; class extends from &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject&quot;&gt;BaseObject&lt;/a&gt; and supports &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/concept-events&quot;&gt;events&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/concept-behaviors&quot;&gt;behaviors&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-component&quot;&gt;Component&lt;/a&gt;类继承了BaseObject类并支持事件和行为。\r\nIf your class does not need the event or behavior feature, \r\n如果您的类不需要事件或行为功能，\r\nyou should consider using &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject&quot;&gt;BaseObject&lt;/a&gt; as the base class. \r\n您应该考虑使用BaseObject作为基类。\r\nThis is usually the case for classes that represent basic data structures.\r\n这种类通常用来表示基本的数据结构。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Object Configuration&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n对象配置\r\nThe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject&quot;&gt;BaseObject&lt;/a&gt; class introduces a uniform way of configuring objects. \r\nBaseObject类引入了一种配置对象的统一方法。\r\nAny descendant class of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject&quot;&gt;BaseObject&lt;/a&gt; should declare its constructor (if needed) in the following way so that it can be properly configured:\r\nBaseObject的任何子类都应按以下方式声明其构造函数（如果需要），以便正确配置它：\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;class MyClass extends \\yii\\base\\BaseObject\r\n{\r\n    public function __construct($param1, $param2, $config = [])\r\n    {\r\n        // ... initialization before configuration is applied\r\n\r\n        parent::__construct($config);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    public function init()\r\n    {\r\n        parent::init();\r\n\r\n        // ... initialization after configuration is applied\r\n    }\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;In the above, the last parameter of the constructor must take a configuration array that contains name-value pairs for initializing the properties at the end of the constructor. \r\n在上面，构造函数的最后一个参数必须采用一个配置数组，该数组包含用于在构造函数末尾初始化属性的名称-值对。\r\nYou can override the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject#init()-detail&quot;&gt;init()&lt;/a&gt; method to do initialization work that should be done after the configuration has been applied.\r\n你可以重写 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-baseobject#init()-detail&quot;&gt;init()&lt;/a&gt; 方法来执行一些需要在配置生效后进行的初始化工作。\r\nBy following this convention, \r\n遵守这个条约，\r\nyou will be able to create and configure new objects using a configuration array:\r\n你可以用配置数组创建和配置新对象\r\n\r\n$object = Yii::createObject([\r\n    &amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;MyClass&amp;#39;,\r\n    &amp;#39;property1&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;abc&amp;#39;,\r\n    &amp;#39;property2&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;cde&amp;#39;,\r\n], [$param1, $param2]);\r\n\r\nMore details about configurations can be found in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/concept-configurations&quot;&gt;Configurations&lt;/a&gt; section.\r\n更多有关配置的细节可以在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/zh-cn/concept-configurations&quot;&gt;配置&lt;/a&gt;章节找到。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;﻿Events&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n事件\r\nIn Yii 1, events were created by defining an &lt;code&gt;on&lt;/code&gt;-method (e.g., &lt;code&gt;onBeforeSave&lt;/code&gt;). \r\n在Yii 1中，通过定义on方法（例如onBeforeSave）创建事件。\r\nIn Yii 2, you can now use any event name. \r\n在Yii 2中，现在可以使用任何事件名称。\r\nYou trigger an event by calling the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-component#trigger()-detail&quot;&gt;trigger()&lt;/a&gt; method:\r\n通过调用trigger（）方法触发事件：\r\n\r\n$event = new \\yii\\base\\Event;\r\n$component-&amp;gt;trigger($eventName, $event);\r\n\r\nTo attach a handler to an event, use the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-component#on()-detail&quot;&gt;on()&lt;/a&gt; method:\r\n要将处理程序附加到事件，请使用on（）方法：\r\n\r\n$component-&amp;gt;on($eventName, $handler);\r\n// To detach the handler, use:\r\n// $component-&amp;gt;off($eventName, $handler);\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;There are many enhancements to the event features. For more details, please refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/concept-events&quot;&gt;Events&lt;/a&gt; section.\r\n事件功能有许多增强。有关更多详细信息，请参阅事件部分。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Path Aliases&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n路径别名\r\nYii 2.0 expands the usage of path aliases to both file/directory paths and URLs. \r\nYii 2.0将路径别名的使用扩展到文件/目录路径和url。\r\nYii 2.0 also now requires an alias name to start with the &lt;code&gt;@&lt;/code&gt; character, to differentiate aliases from normal file/directory paths or URLs. \r\nYii 2.0现在还要求别名以@字符开头，以区分别名与普通文件/目录路径或URL。\r\nFor example, the alias &lt;code&gt;@yii&lt;/code&gt; refers to the Yii installation directory. \r\n例如 &lt;code&gt;@yii&lt;/code&gt; 就是指向 Yii 安装目录的别名\r\nPath aliases are supported in most places in the Yii core code. \r\n绝大多数 Yii 核心代码都支持别名。\r\nFor example, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-caching-filecache#$cachePath-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\caching\\FileCache::$cachePath&lt;/a&gt; can take both a path alias and a normal directory path.\r\n例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-caching-filecache#$cachePath-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\caching\\FileCache::$cachePath&lt;/a&gt; 就同时支持路径别名或普通的目录地址。\r\nA path alias is also closely related to a class namespace. \r\n路径别名也和类的命名空间密切相关。\r\nIt is recommended that a path alias be defined for each root namespace, thereby allowing you to use Yii class autoloader without any further configuration. \r\n建议为每个根命名空间定义一个路径别名，从而无须额外配置，便可使用 Yii 的类自动加载机制。\r\nFor example, because &lt;code&gt;@yii&lt;/code&gt; refers to the Yii installation directory, a class like &lt;code&gt;yii\\web\\Request&lt;/code&gt; can be autoloaded. \r\n例如，因为@yii指向yii安装目录，所以可以自动加载类似yii\\web\\Request的类。\r\nIf you use a third party library, such as the Zend Framework, you may define a path alias &lt;code&gt;@Zend&lt;/code&gt; that refers to that framework&amp;#39;s installation directory. \r\n如果使用第三方库（如Zend Framework），则可以定义一个路径别名 &lt;code&gt;@Zend&lt;/code&gt;，该路径别名&lt;code&gt;@Zend&lt;/code&gt;引用该框架的安装目录。\r\nOnce you&amp;#39;ve done that, Yii will be able to autoload any class in that Zend Framework library, too.\r\n一旦你做到了，Yii也可以自动加载Zend框架库中的任何类。\r\nMore on path aliases can be found in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/concept-aliases&quot;&gt;Aliases&lt;/a&gt; section.\r\n有关路径别名的详细信息，请参见&amp;ldquo;别名&amp;rdquo;章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Views&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n视图\r\nThe most significant change about views in Yii 2 is \r\nyii 2 中关于视图最重要的变化是\r\nthat the special variable &lt;code&gt;$this&lt;/code&gt; in a view no longer refers to the current controller or widget. \r\n视图中特殊变量$this 不再指向当前的controller 或者 widget\r\nInstead, &lt;code&gt;$this&lt;/code&gt; now refers to a &lt;em&gt;view&lt;/em&gt; object, \r\n相反，$this 指向的是一个&lt;em&gt;view&lt;/em&gt; object，\r\na new concept introduced in 2.0. \r\n这是2.0中引入的一个新概念。\r\nThe &lt;em&gt;view&lt;/em&gt; object is of type &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-view&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\View&lt;/a&gt;, \r\n&lt;em&gt;view&lt;/em&gt; object的类型是 yii\\web\\View，\r\nwhich represents the view part of the MVC pattern. \r\n他代表了 MVC 模式中的视图部分。\r\nIf you want to access the controller or widget in a view,\r\n如果要访问视图中的controller或widget，\r\nyou can use &lt;code&gt;$this-&amp;gt;context&lt;/code&gt;.\r\n可以用$this-&amp;gt;context 。\r\nTo render a partial view within another view, \r\n要在其他视图里渲染一个局部视图,\r\nyou use &lt;code&gt;$this-&amp;gt;render()&lt;/code&gt;, not &lt;code&gt;$this-&amp;gt;renderPartial()&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n使用的是&lt;code&gt;$this-&amp;gt;render()，而不是$this-&amp;gt;renderPartial()。&lt;/code&gt;\r\nThe call to &lt;code&gt;render&lt;/code&gt; also now has to be explicitly echoed, as the &lt;code&gt;render()&lt;/code&gt; method returns the rendering result, rather than directly displaying it. \r\n&lt;code&gt;render()&lt;/code&gt; 现在只返回渲染结果，而不是直接显示它，所以现在你必须显式地把它 &lt;strong&gt;echo&lt;/strong&gt; 出来。\r\nFor example:\r\n像这样的：\r\n&lt;strong&gt;echo&lt;/strong&gt; $this-&amp;gt;render(&amp;#39;_item&amp;#39;, [&amp;#39;item&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $item]);\r\nBesides using PHP as the primary template language, \r\n除了使用PHP作为主要模板语言之外，\r\nYii 2.0 is also equipped with official support for two popular template engines: \r\nYii 2.0还配备了两个流行模板引擎的官方支持：\r\nSmarty and Twig. \r\nThe Prado template engine is no longer supported. \r\nPrado 模板引擎不再被支持。\r\nTo use these template engines, \r\n要使用这些模版引擎，\r\nyou need to configure the &lt;code&gt;view&lt;/code&gt; application component by setting the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-view#$renderers-detail&quot;&gt;View::$renderers&lt;/a&gt; property. \r\n你需要配置 &lt;code&gt;view&lt;/code&gt; 应用组件， 给它设置 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-view#$renderers-detail&quot;&gt;View::$renderers&lt;/a&gt; 属性。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-template-engines&quot;&gt;Template Engines&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n具体请参阅&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-template-engines&quot;&gt;Template Engines&lt;/a&gt;章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Models&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n模型\r\nYii 2.0 uses &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Model&lt;/a&gt; as the base model, \r\nYii 2.0 使用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Model&lt;/a&gt; 作为模型基类，\r\nsimilar to &lt;code&gt;CModel&lt;/code&gt; in 1.1. \r\n类似于1.1中的CModel。\r\nThe class &lt;code&gt;CFormModel&lt;/code&gt; has been dropped entirely. \r\n类CFormModel已完全删除。\r\nInstead, in Yii 2 you should extend &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Model&lt;/a&gt; to create a form model class.\r\n替代这一做法，在Yii 2中，您应该扩展Yii\\base\\Model来创建表单模型类。\r\nYii 2.0 introduces a new method called &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#scenarios()-detail&quot;&gt;scenarios()&lt;/a&gt; to declare supported scenarios, \r\nYii 2.0引入了一个名为scenarios（）的新方法来声明支持的场景，\r\nand to indicate under which scenario an attribute needs to be validated, \r\n并指示在哪个场景下需要验证属性，\r\ncan be considered as safe or not, etc. For example:\r\n可以认为是安全的或不安全的，例如：\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;public function scenarios()&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; return [&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;#39;backend&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;email&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;role&amp;#39;],&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;#39;frontend&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;email&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;!role&amp;#39;],&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; ];&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;In the above, two scenarios are declared: \r\n在上面，声明了两个场景：\r\n&lt;code&gt;backend&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;frontend&lt;/code&gt;. For the &lt;code&gt;backend&lt;/code&gt; scenario, \r\n&lt;code&gt;backend&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;frontend&lt;/code&gt;。对于 &lt;code&gt;backend&lt;/code&gt;场景，\r\nboth the &lt;code&gt;email&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;role&lt;/code&gt; attributes are safe, \r\n&lt;code&gt;email&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;role&lt;/code&gt; 这俩个属性都是安全的，\r\nand can be massively assigned. \r\n且能进行批量赋值。\r\nFor the &lt;code&gt;frontend&lt;/code&gt; scenario, &lt;code&gt;email&lt;/code&gt; can be massively assigned while &lt;code&gt;role&lt;/code&gt; cannot. \r\n对于 &lt;code&gt;frontend&lt;/code&gt; 场景，&lt;code&gt;email&lt;/code&gt; 能批量赋值而 &lt;code&gt;role&lt;/code&gt; 不能。\r\nBoth &lt;code&gt;email&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;role&lt;/code&gt; should be validated using rules.\r\n&lt;code&gt;email&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;role&lt;/code&gt; 都应该使用规则进行验证。\r\nThe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#rules()-detail&quot;&gt;rules()&lt;/a&gt; method is still used to declare the validation rules. \r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#rules()-detail&quot;&gt;rules()&lt;/a&gt; 方法仍用于声明验证规则。\r\nNote that due to the introduction of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#scenarios()-detail&quot;&gt;scenarios()&lt;/a&gt;, there is no longer an &lt;code&gt;unsafe&lt;/code&gt; validator.\r\n注意，由于引入了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#scenarios()-detail&quot;&gt;scenarios()&lt;/a&gt;，现在已经没有 &lt;code&gt;unsafe&lt;/code&gt; 验证器了。\r\nIn most cases, you do not need to override &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#scenarios()-detail&quot;&gt;scenarios()&lt;/a&gt; if the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#rules()-detail&quot;&gt;rules()&lt;/a&gt; method fully specifies the scenarios that will exist, \r\n大多数情况下，如果 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#rules()-detail&quot;&gt;rules()&lt;/a&gt; 方法内已经完整地指定场景了， 那就不必覆写 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-model#scenarios()-detail&quot;&gt;scenarios()&lt;/a&gt;，\r\nand if there is no need to declare &lt;code&gt;unsafe&lt;/code&gt; attributes.\r\n也不必去声明&lt;code&gt;unsafe&lt;/code&gt; 属性。\r\nTo learn more details about models, please refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-models&quot;&gt;Models&lt;/a&gt; section.\r\n要了解有关模型的更多详细信息，请参阅&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-models&quot;&gt;Models&lt;/a&gt;部分。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Controllers&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n控制器\r\nYii 2.0 uses &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-controller&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\Controller&lt;/a&gt; as the base controller class, \r\nyii 2.0 使用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-controller&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\Controller&lt;/a&gt; 作为控制器基类，\r\nwhich is similar to &lt;code&gt;CController&lt;/code&gt; in Yii 1.1. \r\n它类似于 yii 1.1 中的 &lt;code&gt;CController 。&lt;/code&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-action&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Action&lt;/a&gt; is the base class for action classes.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-action&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Action&lt;/a&gt; 是action类的基类。\r\nThe most obvious impact of these changes on your code is \r\n这些更改对代码最明显的影响是\r\nthat a controller action should return the content that you want to render instead of echoing it:\r\n应该返回（return）要渲染的内容而不是输出（echo）它：\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;public function actionView($id)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; $model = \\app\\models\\Post::findOne($id);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; if ($model) {&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; return $this-&amp;gt;render(&amp;#39;view&amp;#39;, [&amp;#39;model&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $model]);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; } else {&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; throw new \\yii\\web\\NotFoundHttpException;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; }&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Please refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-controllers&quot;&gt;Controllers&lt;/a&gt; section for more details about controllers.\r\n有关控制器更多详细，请参考 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-controllers&quot;&gt;Controllers&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Widgets&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n小部件\r\nYii 2.0 uses &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-widget&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Widget&lt;/a&gt; as the base widget class, \r\nyii 2.0 使用  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-widget&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\Widget&lt;/a&gt; 作为 widget类的基类，\r\nsimilar to &lt;code&gt;CWidget&lt;/code&gt; in Yii 1.1.\r\n类似于1.1 中的&lt;code&gt;CWidget。&lt;/code&gt;\r\nTo get better support for the framework in IDEs, \r\n为了更好地支持ide中的框架，\r\nYii 2.0 introduces a new syntax for using widgets. \r\nyii 2.0 引入了使用 widgets 的新语法。\r\nThe static methods &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-widget#begin()-detail&quot;&gt;begin()&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-widget#end()-detail&quot;&gt;end()&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-widget#widget()-detail&quot;&gt;widget()&lt;/a&gt; have been introduced, to be used like so:\r\n已经引入了静态方法begin（）、end（）和widget（），如下所示：&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;use yii\\widgets\\Menu;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;use yii\\widgets\\ActiveForm;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;// Note that you have to &amp;quot;echo&amp;quot; the result to display it&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;echo Menu::widget([&amp;#39;items&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $items]);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;// Passing an array to initialize the object properties&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;$form = ActiveForm::begin([&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;#39;options&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;form-horizontal&amp;#39;],&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;#39;fieldConfig&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;inputOptions&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;input-xlarge&amp;#39;]],&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;]);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;... form input fields here ...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ActiveForm::end();&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Please refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-widgets&quot;&gt;Widgets&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多详细请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-widgets&quot;&gt;Widgets&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Themes&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n主题\r\nThemes work completely differently in 2.0. \r\n主题在2.0中的工作方式完全不同。\r\nThey are now based on a path mapping mechanism that maps a source view file path to a themed view file path. \r\n它们现在基于&lt;strong&gt;路径映射机制&lt;/strong&gt;，该机制会把一个源视图文件的路径映射到一个主题视图文件路径。\r\nFor example, \r\nif the path map for a theme is &lt;code&gt;[&amp;#39;/web/views&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;/web/themes/basic&amp;#39;]&lt;/code&gt;, \r\n如果主题的路径映射为[&amp;#39;/web/views&amp;#39;=&amp;gt;&amp;#39;/web/themes/basic&amp;#39;]，\r\nthen the themed version for the view file &lt;code&gt;/web/views/site/index.php&lt;/code&gt; will be &lt;code&gt;/web/themes/basic/site/index.php&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n那么视图文件/web/views/site/index.php的主题版本将是/web/themes/basic/site/index.php。\r\nFor this reason, themes can now be applied to any view file,\r\n因此，主题现在可以应用于任何视图文件，\r\neven a view rendered outside of the context of a controller or a widget.\r\n甚至在controller或widget上下文之外渲染的视图。\r\nAlso, there is no more &lt;code&gt;CThemeManager&lt;/code&gt; component. \r\n此外，不再有CThemeManager组件。\r\nInstead, &lt;code&gt;theme&lt;/code&gt; is a configurable property of the &lt;code&gt;view&lt;/code&gt; application component.\r\n取而代之的 &lt;code&gt;theme&lt;/code&gt; 成为了 &lt;code&gt;view&lt;/code&gt; 应用组件的一个可配置属性。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-theming&quot;&gt;Theming&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多详细的请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/output-theming&quot;&gt;Theming&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Console Applications&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n控制台应用\r\nConsole applications are now organized as controllers,like Web applications. \r\nConsole applications现在像Web应用程序一样被组织为控制器。\r\nConsole controllers should extend from &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-console-controller&quot;&gt;yii\\console\\Controller&lt;/a&gt;, \r\nConsole controllers应该从yii\\Console\\Controller扩展，\r\nsimilar to &lt;code&gt;CConsoleCommand&lt;/code&gt; in 1.1.\r\n类似于1.1中的CConsoleCommand。\r\nTo run a console command, \r\n要运行console 命令，\r\nuse &lt;code&gt;yii &amp;lt;route&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, where &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;route&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; stands for a controller route (e.g. &lt;code&gt;sitemap/index&lt;/code&gt;). \r\n使用 &lt;code&gt;yii &amp;lt;route&amp;gt;，&lt;/code&gt;其中 &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;route&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; 代表控制器的路由（如 &lt;code&gt;sitemap/index&lt;/code&gt;）。\r\nAdditional anonymous arguments are passed as the parameters to the corresponding controller action method, \r\n额外的匿名参数传递到对应的控制器操作方法， \r\nwhile named arguments are parsed according to the declarations in &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-console-controller#options()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\console\\Controller::options()&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n而命名参数则根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-console-controller#options()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\console\\Controller::options()&lt;/a&gt;中的声明进行分析。\r\nYii 2.0 supports automatic generation of command help information from comment blocks.\r\nYii 2.0支持从注释块自动生成命令帮助信息。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-console&quot;&gt;Console Commands&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多细节请参阅&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-console&quot;&gt;Console Commands&lt;/a&gt;章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;I18N&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n国际化\r\nYii 2.0 removes the built-in date formatter and number formatter pieces in favor of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://pecl.php.net/package/intl&quot;&gt;PECL intl PHP module&lt;/a&gt;.\r\nYii 2.0删除了内置的日期格式器和数字格式器，取而代之的是PECL intl PHP模块。\r\nMessage translation is now performed via the &lt;code&gt;i18n&lt;/code&gt; application component. \r\n消息翻译现在由 &lt;code&gt;i18n&lt;/code&gt; 应用组件执行。\r\nThis component manages a set of message sources, \r\n该组件管理一组消息源，\r\nwhich allows you to use different message sources based on message categories.\r\n允许您根据消息类别使用不同的消息源。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-i18n&quot;&gt;Internationalization&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多的信息请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-i18n&quot;&gt;Internationalization&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Action Filters&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n动作过滤器\r\nAction filters are implemented via behaviors now. \r\nAction filters现在通过行为（behavior）来实现。\r\nTo define a new, custom filter, extend from &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-base-actionfilter&quot;&gt;yii\\base\\ActionFilter&lt;/a&gt;. \r\n要定义新的custom filter，请从yii\\base\\ActionFilter扩展。\r\nTo use a filter, attach the filter class to the controller as a behavior. \r\n要使用一个filter，请将filter class作为behavior附加到controller。\r\nFor example, \r\nto use the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-filters-accesscontrol&quot;&gt;yii\\filters\\AccessControl&lt;/a&gt; filter,\r\n要使用&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-filters-accesscontrol&quot;&gt;yii\\filters\\AccessControl&lt;/a&gt; filter，\r\nyou would have the following code in a controller:\r\n你应该在controller内添加如下代码：\r\npublic function behaviors()\r\n{\r\n    return [\r\n        &amp;#39;access&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n            &amp;#39;class&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;yii\\filters\\AccessControl&amp;#39;,\r\n            &amp;#39;rules&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [\r\n                [&amp;#39;allow&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; true, &amp;#39;actions&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;admin&amp;#39;], &amp;#39;roles&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;@&amp;#39;]],\r\n            ],\r\n        ],\r\n    ];\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Please refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-filters&quot;&gt;Filtering&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多详细信息请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-filters&quot;&gt;Filtering&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Assets&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n前端资源\r\nYii 2.0 introduces a new concept called &lt;em&gt;asset bundle&lt;/em&gt; \r\nYii 2.0引入了一个叫做资产包的新概念\r\nthat replaces the script package concept found in Yii 1.1.\r\n资产包取代了Yii 1.1中的脚本包概念。\r\nAn asset bundle is a collection of asset files (e.g. JavaScript files, CSS files, image files, etc.) within a directory. \r\n资产包是目录中资产文件（如JavaScript文件、CSS文件、图像文件等）的集合。\r\nEach asset bundle is represented as a class extending &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-assetbundle&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\AssetBundle&lt;/a&gt;. \r\n每个资产包都表示为扩展yii\\web\\asset bundle的类。\r\nBy registering an asset bundle via &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-assetbundle#register()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\AssetBundle::register()&lt;/a&gt;,\r\n通过&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-assetbundle#register()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\AssetBundle::register()&lt;/a&gt; 注册一个资产包，\r\nyou make the assets in that bundle accessible via the Web. \r\n您可以通过Web访问该捆绑包中的资产。\r\nUnlike in Yii 1, the page registering the bundle will automatically contain the references to the JavaScript and CSS files specified in that bundle.\r\n与Yii 1不同，注册了资源包的页面会自动包含和引用资源包内指定的 JS 和 CSS 文件。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-assets&quot;&gt;Managing Assets&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多细节请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-assets&quot;&gt;Managing Assets&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Helpers&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n助手类\r\nYii 2.0 introduces many commonly used static helper classes, including.\r\nYii 2.0引入了许多常用的静态助手类，包括.\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-helpers-html&quot;&gt;yii\\helpers\\Html&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-helpers-arrayhelper&quot;&gt;yii\\helpers\\ArrayHelper&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-helpers-stringhelper&quot;&gt;yii\\helpers\\StringHelper&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-helpers-filehelper&quot;&gt;yii\\helpers\\FileHelper&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-helpers-json&quot;&gt;yii\\helpers\\Json&lt;/a&gt;\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/helper-overview&quot;&gt;Helper Overview&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多细节请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/helper-overview&quot;&gt;Helper Overview&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Forms&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n表单\r\nYii 2.0 introduces the &lt;em&gt;field&lt;/em&gt; concept for building a form using &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-activeform&quot;&gt;yii\\widgets\\ActiveForm&lt;/a&gt;. \r\nYii 2.0引入了使用Yii\\widgets\\ActiveForm构建表单的字段概念。\r\nA field is a container consisting of a label, an input, an error message, and/or a hint text. \r\n一个field是由一个label，一个input，一个错误消息，and/or 一个 提示文本组成的容器。\r\nA field is represented as an &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-activefield&quot;&gt;ActiveField&lt;/a&gt; object. \r\n一个field 表示一个&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-widgets-activefield&quot;&gt;ActiveField&lt;/a&gt; 对象。\r\nUsing fields, you can build a form more cleanly than before:\r\n使用fields建立表单的过程比以前更整洁利落：\r\n\r\n&amp;lt;?php $form = yii\\widgets\\ActiveForm::begin(); ?&amp;gt;\r\n    &amp;lt;?= $form-&amp;gt;field($model, &amp;#39;username&amp;#39;) ?&amp;gt;\r\n    &amp;lt;?= $form-&amp;gt;field($model, &amp;#39;password&amp;#39;)-&amp;gt;passwordInput() ?&amp;gt;\r\n    &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;form-group&amp;quot;&amp;gt;\r\n        &amp;lt;?= Html::submitButton(&amp;#39;Login&amp;#39;) ?&amp;gt;\r\n    &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;lt;?php yii\\widgets\\ActiveForm::end(); ?&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Please refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/input-forms&quot;&gt;Creating Forms&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多细节请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/input-forms&quot;&gt;Creating Forms&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Query Builder&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n查询生成器\r\nIn 1.1, query building was scattered among several classes,\r\nYii 1.1 中，查询语句的生成分散在多个类中，\r\nincluding &lt;code&gt;CDbCommand&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;CDbCriteria&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code&gt;CDbCommandBuilder&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n包括 &lt;code&gt;CDbCommand&lt;/code&gt;，&lt;code&gt;CDbCriteria&lt;/code&gt; 以及 &lt;code&gt;CDbCommandBuilder&lt;/code&gt;。\r\nYii 2.0 represents a DB query in terms of a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-query&quot;&gt;Query&lt;/a&gt; object \r\nYii 2.0 以 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-query&quot;&gt;Query&lt;/a&gt; 对象的形式表示一个数据库查询，\r\nthat can be turned into a SQL statement with the help of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-querybuilder&quot;&gt;QueryBuilder&lt;/a&gt; behind the scene. \r\n这个对象使用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-querybuilder&quot;&gt;QueryBuilder&lt;/a&gt; 在幕后生成 SQL 语句。\r\nFor example:\r\n$query = new \\yii\\db\\Query();\r\n$query-&amp;gt;select(&amp;#39;id, name&amp;#39;)\r\n      -&amp;gt;from(&amp;#39;user&amp;#39;)\r\n      -&amp;gt;limit(10);\r\n\r\n$command = $query-&amp;gt;createCommand();\r\n$sql = $command-&amp;gt;sql;\r\n$rows = $command-&amp;gt;queryAll();&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Best of all, \r\n最棒的是，\r\nsuch query building methods can also be used when working with &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-active-record&quot;&gt;Active Record&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n这些查询生成方法还可以和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-active-record&quot;&gt;Active Record&lt;/a&gt; 配合使用。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-query-builder&quot;&gt;Query Builder&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多细节请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-query-builder&quot;&gt;Query Builder&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Active Record&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n活动记录\r\nYii 2.0 introduces a lot of changes to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-active-record&quot;&gt;Active Record&lt;/a&gt;. \r\nYii 2.0为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-active-record&quot;&gt;Active Record&lt;/a&gt;引入了许多更改。\r\nThe two most obvious ones involve query building and relational query handling.\r\n两个最显而易见的改动分别涉及查询语句的生成（query building）和关联查询的处理（relational query handling）。\r\nThe &lt;code&gt;CDbCriteria&lt;/code&gt; class in 1.1 is replaced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activequery&quot;&gt;yii\\db\\ActiveQuery&lt;/a&gt; in Yii 2. \r\n1.1中的&lt;code&gt;CDbCriteria类被Yii 2 中的&lt;/code&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activequery&quot;&gt;yii\\db\\ActiveQuery&lt;/a&gt; 替换。\r\nThat class extends from &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-query&quot;&gt;yii\\db\\Query&lt;/a&gt;, and thus inherits all query building methods. \r\n该类扩展自yii\\db\\Query，因此继承了所有查询生成方法。\r\nYou call &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activerecord#find()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\db\\ActiveRecord::find()&lt;/a&gt; to start building a query:\r\n调用&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activerecord#find()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\db\\ActiveRecord::find()&lt;/a&gt; 开始生成查询：\r\n// To retrieve all *active* customers and order them by their ID:\r\n$customers = Customer::find()\r\n    -&amp;gt;where([&amp;#39;status&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; $active])\r\n    -&amp;gt;orderBy(&amp;#39;id&amp;#39;)\r\n    -&amp;gt;all();&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;To declare a relation, \r\n要声明一个关联关系，\r\nsimply define a getter method that returns an &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activequery&quot;&gt;ActiveQuery&lt;/a&gt; object. \r\n只需简单定义一个返回 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activequery&quot;&gt;ActiveQuery&lt;/a&gt; 对象的getter方法。\r\nThe property name defined by the getter represents the relation name.\r\ngetter 方法定义的属性名代表关联表名称\r\nFor example, \r\nthe following code declares an &lt;code&gt;orders&lt;/code&gt; relation (in 1.1, you would have to declare relations in a central place &lt;code&gt;relations()&lt;/code&gt;):\r\n下面的代码声明了一个orders关系（在1.1中，您必须在一个中心位置relations（）中声明关系）：\r\n\r\nclass Customer extends \\yii\\db\\ActiveRecord\r\n{\r\n    public function getOrders()\r\n    {\r\n        return $this-&amp;gt;hasMany(&amp;#39;Order&amp;#39;, [&amp;#39;customer_id&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;id&amp;#39;]);\r\n    }\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Now you can use &lt;code&gt;$customer-&amp;gt;orders&lt;/code&gt; to access a customer&amp;#39;s orders from the related table. \r\n现在您可以使用$customer-&amp;gt;orders从关联表中访问客户的订单。\r\nYou can also use the following code to perform an on-the-fly relational query with a customized query condition:\r\n你还可以用以下代码进行一场指定条件的实时关联查询：\r\n$orders = $customer-&amp;gt;getOrders()-&amp;gt;andWhere(&amp;#39;status=1&amp;#39;)-&amp;gt;all();&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;When eager loading a relation, \r\n当贪婪加载一段关联关系时，\r\nYii 2.0 does it differently from 1.1. \r\nYii 2.0 和 1.1 的操作不同。\r\nIn particular, in 1.1 a JOIN query would be created to select both the primary and the relational records. \r\n特别是，在 1.1 中使用一条 JOIN 语句同时查询主表和关联表记录。\r\nIn Yii 2.0, two SQL statements are executed without using JOIN: the first statement brings back the primary records \r\n在 Yii 2.0 中会使用两个没有 JOIN 的 SQL 语句：第一条语句取回主表记录，\r\nand the second brings back the relational records by filtering with the primary keys of the primary records.\r\n 第二条通过主表记录经主键筛选后查询关联表记录。\r\nInstead of returning &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activerecord&quot;&gt;ActiveRecord&lt;/a&gt; objects, you may chain the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activequerytrait#asArray()-detail&quot;&gt;asArray()&lt;/a&gt; method when building a query to return a large number of records. This will cause the query result to be returned as arrays, \r\n当生成返回大量记录的查询时，可以链式调用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activequerytrait#asArray()-detail&quot;&gt;asArray()&lt;/a&gt; 方法， 这样会以数组的形式返回查询结果，而不必返回 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-activerecord&quot;&gt;ActiveRecord&lt;/a&gt; 对象，\r\nwhich can significantly reduce the needed CPU time and memory if large number of records . \r\n这能显著降低因大量记录读取所消耗的 CPU 时间和内存。\r\nFor example:\r\n$customers = Customer::find()-&amp;gt;asArray()-&amp;gt;all();\r\n\r\nAnother change is that you can&amp;#39;t define attribute default values through public properties anymore. \r\n另一个改变是你不能再通过公共属性定义属性（Attribute）的默认值了。\r\nIf you need those,\r\n如果你需要这样做，\r\nyou should set them in the init method of your record class.\r\n您应该在record类的init方法中设置它们。\r\npublic function init()\r\n{\r\n    parent::init();\r\n    $this-&amp;gt;status = self::STATUS_NEW;\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;There were some problems with overriding the constructor of an ActiveRecord class in 1.1. \r\n1.1中重写ActiveRecord类的constructor 会出现些问题。\r\nThese are not present in version 2.0 anymore. \r\n2.0版本中就不会存在这些问题。\r\nNote that when adding parameters to the constructor you might have to override &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-baseactiverecord#instantiate()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\db\\ActiveRecord::instantiate()&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n注意，向constructor添加参数到时你必须override &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-baseactiverecord#instantiate()-detail&quot;&gt;yii\\db\\ActiveRecord::instantiate()。&lt;/a&gt;\r\nThere are many other changes and enhancements to Active Record.\r\nActive Record还有许多其他更改和增强功能。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-active-record&quot;&gt;Active Record&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多细节请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/db-active-record&quot;&gt;Active Record&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Active Record Behaviors&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n活动记录行为\r\nIn 2.0, we have dropped the base behavior class &lt;code&gt;CActiveRecordBehavior&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n在2.0中，我们删除了基本行为类&lt;code&gt;CActiveRecordBehavior&lt;/code&gt;。\r\nIf you want to create an Active Record Behavior, \r\n如果你要创建一个Active Record Behavior。\r\nyou will have to extend directly from &lt;code&gt;yii\\base\\Behavior&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n必须直接从&lt;code&gt;yii\\base\\Behavior&lt;/code&gt;扩展。\r\nIf the behavior class needs to respond to some events of the owner, \r\n如果behavior类需要响应owner的某些事件，\r\nyou have to override the &lt;code&gt;events()&lt;/code&gt; method like the following:\r\n必须override &lt;code&gt;events()&lt;/code&gt;方法，如下所示：\r\nnamespace app\\components;\r\n\r\nuse yii\\db\\ActiveRecord;\r\nuse yii\\base\\Behavior;\r\n\r\nclass MyBehavior extends Behavior\r\n{\r\n    // ...\r\n\r\n    public function events()\r\n    {\r\n        return [\r\n            ActiveRecord::EVENT_BEFORE_VALIDATE =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;beforeValidate&amp;#39;,\r\n        ];\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    public function beforeValidate($event)\r\n    {\r\n        // ...\r\n    }\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;User and IdentityInterface&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n用户及身份验证接口\r\nThe &lt;code&gt;CWebUser&lt;/code&gt; class in 1.1 is now replaced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-user&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\User&lt;/a&gt;,and there is no more &lt;code&gt;CUserIdentity&lt;/code&gt; class. \r\n1.1中的CWebUser类现在被yii\\web\\User替换，不再有cuseridenty类。\r\nInstead, you should implement the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-identityinterface&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\IdentityInterface&lt;/a&gt; which is much more straightforward to use. \r\n相反，您应该实现 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-web-identityinterface&quot;&gt;yii\\web\\IdentityInterface&lt;/a&gt;，它更易于使用。\r\nThe advanced project template provides such an example.\r\n高级项目模板提供了这样一个示例。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/security-authentication&quot;&gt;Authentication&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/security-authorization&quot;&gt;Authorization&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/extension/yiisoft/yii2-app-advanced/doc/guide&quot;&gt;Advanced Project Template&lt;/a&gt; sections for more details.\r\n更多细节请参看&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/security-authentication&quot;&gt;Authentication&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/security-authorization&quot;&gt;Authorization&lt;/a&gt;, 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/extension/yiisoft/yii2-app-advanced/doc/guide&quot;&gt;Advanced Project Template&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;URL Management\r\nURL 管理\r\nURL management in Yii 2 is similar to that in 1.1. \r\nYii 2中的URL management与1.1中的类似。\r\nA major enhancement is that URL management now supports optional parameters. \r\n一个主要的改进是现在的 URL management支持&lt;strong&gt;可选参数&lt;/strong&gt;了。\r\nFor example, \r\nif you have a rule declared as follows, \r\n如果你有一条规则声明如下，\r\nthen it will match both &lt;code&gt;post/popular&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;post/1/popular&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n那么它将同时匹配&lt;code&gt;post/popular&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;post/1/popular 。&lt;/code&gt;\r\nIn 1.1, you would have had to use two rules to achieve the same goal.\r\n在1.1中，您必须使用两个规则来实现相同的目标。\r\n[\r\n    &amp;#39;pattern&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;post/&amp;lt;page:\\d+&amp;gt;/&amp;lt;tag&amp;gt;&amp;#39;,\r\n    &amp;#39;route&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;post/index&amp;#39;,\r\n    &amp;#39;defaults&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; [&amp;#39;page&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; 1],\r\n]&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Please refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/runtime-routing&quot;&gt;Url manager docs&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多的细节请参看&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/runtime-routing&quot;&gt;Url manager docs&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;An important change in the naming convention for routes is that camel case names of controllers and actions are now converted to lower case where each word is separated by a hypen,\r\n一个重要变化是路由命名的约定， 现在的控制器和动作的驼峰命名会被转换成小写字母， 其中每个单词由一个专有的连字号(-)分隔\r\ne.g. the controller id for the &lt;code&gt;CamelCaseController&lt;/code&gt; will be &lt;code&gt;camel-case&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n例如：controller id &lt;code&gt;CamelCaseController 会转变为 camel-case&lt;/code&gt;\r\nSee the section about &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-controllers#controller-ids&quot;&gt;controller IDs&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-controllers.md#action-ids&quot;&gt;action IDs&lt;/a&gt; for more details.\r\n更多细节看有关&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-controllers#controller-ids&quot;&gt;controller IDs&lt;/a&gt; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-controllers.md#action-ids&quot;&gt;action IDs&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Using Yii 1.1 and 2.x together\r\n同时使用 Yii 1.1 和 2.x \r\nIf you have legacy Yii 1.1 code that you want to use together with Yii 2.0,\r\n如果你有一些遗留的 Yii 1.1 代码，需要跟 Yii 2.0 一起使用，\r\nplease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-yii-integration#using-both-yii2-yii1&quot;&gt;Using Yii 1.1 and 2.0 Together&lt;/a&gt; section.\r\n请参考 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-yii-integration#using-both-yii2-yii1&quot;&gt;Using Yii 1.1 and 2.0 Together&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;What do you need to know&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n你需要知道什么\r\nThe Yii learning curve is not as steep as other PHP frameworks but still there are some things you should learn before starting with Yii.\r\nYii学习曲线并不像其他PHP框架那么陡峭，但是在开始使用Yii之前，仍然有一些东西需要学习。\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;PHP&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nYii is a PHP framework so make sure you &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/langref.php&quot;&gt;read and understand language reference&lt;/a&gt;. \r\nYii 是一个 PHP 框架，因此请确保您 &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/zh/langref.php&quot;&gt;阅读并理解语言参考&lt;/a&gt;。\r\nWhen developing with Yii you will be writing code in an object oriented fashion, \r\n用 Yii 进行开发时，您将以面向对象的方式编写代码，\r\nso make sure you are familiar with &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.oop5.basic.php&quot;&gt;Classes and Objects&lt;/a&gt; as well as &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/language.namespaces.php&quot;&gt;namespaces&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n因此，请确保您熟悉类、对象以及名称空间。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Object oriented programming&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n面向对象程序\r\nBasic understanding of object oriented programming is required. \r\n需要对面向对象编程有基本的了解。\r\nIf you&amp;#39;re not familiar with it, \r\n如果你不熟悉，\r\ncheck one of the many tutorials available such as &lt;a href=&quot;https://code.tutsplus.com/tutorials/object-oriented-php-for-beginners--net-12762&quot;&gt;the one from tuts+&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n请查看许多可用的教程之一，如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://code.tutsplus.com/tutorials/object-oriented-php-for-beginners--net-12762&quot;&gt;tuts+&lt;/a&gt;。\r\nNote that the more complicated your application is the more advanced OOP concepts you should learn in order to successfully manage that complexity.\r\n请注意，您的应用程序越复杂，您需要学习的更高级的 OOP 概念才能成功 掌握这种复杂度。\r\n请注意，应用程序越复杂，为了成功地管理这种复杂性，您应该学习更高级的OOP概念。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Command line and composer&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n命令行和composer\r\nYii extensively uses de-facto standard PHP package manager, \r\nYii 广泛的用起了标准的php包管理器，\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/&quot;&gt;Composer&lt;/a&gt; so make sure you read and understand its &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/01-basic-usage.md&quot;&gt;guide&lt;/a&gt;. \r\ncomposer, 因此请确保阅读并理解其指南。\r\nIf you are not familiar with using command line it is time to start trying. \r\n如果您不熟悉使用命令行，现在是开始尝试的时候了。\r\nOnce you learn the basics you&amp;#39;ll never want to work without it.\r\n一旦你学会了基本知识，你就会觉的没有了它就感觉工作不方便了。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Installing Yii&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n安装Yii\r\nYou can install Yii in two ways, \r\n你可以用两种方式安装Yii,\r\nusing the &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/&quot;&gt;Composer&lt;/a&gt; package manager or by downloading an archive file.\r\n使用&lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/&quot;&gt;Composer&lt;/a&gt; 包管理器或下载一个存档文件。\r\nThe former is the preferred way, \r\n前者是首选方法，\r\nas it allows you to install new &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-extensions&quot;&gt;extensions&lt;/a&gt; or update Yii by simply running a single command.\r\n因为它允许您通过运行一个命令来安装新的扩展或更新Yii。\r\nStandard installations of Yii result in both the framework and a project template being downloaded and installed.\r\n标准安装完Yii之后，框架和一个项目模板两者都下载并安装好了。\r\nA project template is a working Yii project implementing some basic features, such as login, contact form, etc. \r\n项目模板是一个运行中的Yii项目，它实现了一些基本功能，如登录、联系人表单等。\r\nIts code is organized in a recommended way. Therefore, it can serve as a good starting point for your projects.\r\n它(登录，联系，表单等)的代码是以推荐的方式组织的。因此，它能够适合作为你项目的一个好的起点。\r\nIn this and the next few sections, \r\n在本章节和以后的章节\r\nwe will describe how to install Yii with the so-called &lt;em&gt;Basic Project Template&lt;/em&gt; and how to implement new features on top of this template. \r\n我们会描述如何使用所谓的基本项目模版安装Yii,以及如何在此模版上实现新特征。\r\nYii also provides another template called the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/extension/yiisoft/yii2-app-advanced/doc/guide&quot;&gt;Advanced Project Template&lt;/a&gt; which is better used in a team development environment to develop applications with multiple tiers.\r\nYii还提供了另一个名为高级项目的模版，该模板更好应用于在一个团队开发环境中去开发多层级的应用程序。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Info: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n信息\r\nThe Basic Project Template is suitable for developing 90 percent of Web applications. \r\n基本项目模板适用于开发90%的Web应用程序。\r\nIt differs from the Advanced Project Template mainly in how their code is organized. \r\n它与高级项目模板的主要区别在于它们的代码是如何组织的。\r\nIf you are new to Yii, \r\n如果你是刚接触Yii，\r\nwe strongly recommend you stick to the Basic Project Template for its simplicity yet sufficient functionalities.\r\n我们强烈建议您坚持使用基本项目模板，因为它简单但功能足够。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Installing via Composer&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n通过Composer安装\r\nInstalling Composer\r\n安装Composer\r\nIf you do not already have Composer installed, \r\n如果尚未安装Composer，\r\nyou may do so by following the instructions at &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/download/&quot;&gt;getcomposer.org&lt;/a&gt;. \r\n您可以按照getcomposer.org上的说明进行操作。\r\nOn Linux and Mac OS X, you&amp;#39;ll run the following commands:\r\n在Linux和Mac OS X 操作系统上，您将运行以下命令：\r\ncurl -sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php\r\nmv composer.phar /usr/local/bin/composer\r\n\r\nOn Windows, \r\nWindows操作系统上\r\nyou&amp;#39;ll download and run &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/Composer-Setup.exe&quot;&gt;Composer-Setup.exe&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n你将下载并运行&lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/Composer-Setup.exe&quot;&gt;Composer-Setup.exe&lt;/a&gt; 。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/articles/troubleshooting.md&quot;&gt;Troubleshooting section of the Composer Documentation&lt;/a&gt; if you encounter any problems.\r\n如果遇到任何问题，请到Composer文档的&lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/articles/troubleshooting.md&quot;&gt;Troubleshooting&lt;/a&gt;章节查看。\r\nIf you are new to Composer, \r\n如果你第一次用Composer,\r\nwe also recommend to read at least the &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/01-basic-usage.md&quot;&gt;Basic usage section&lt;/a&gt; of the Composer documentation.\r\n我们还建议至少阅读Composer文档的基本用法部分。\r\nIn this guide all composer commands assume you have installed composer &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md#globally&quot;&gt;globally&lt;/a&gt; so that it is available as the &lt;code&gt;composer&lt;/code&gt; command. \r\n在本指南中，所有的composer命令都假定您已经全局安装了composer，因此它可以作为composer命令使用。\r\nIf you are using the &lt;code&gt;composer.phar&lt;/code&gt; in the local directory instead, you have to adjust the example commands accordingly.\r\n如果您在本地目录中使用 &lt;code&gt;composer.phar&lt;/code&gt;， 则必须相应地调整示例命令。\r\nIf you had Composer already installed before, make sure you use an up to date version. \r\n如果以前已经安装了Composer，请确保使用最新版本。\r\nYou can update Composer by running &lt;code&gt;composer self-update&lt;/code&gt;.\r\n您可以通过运行 &lt;code&gt;composer self-update&lt;/code&gt; 来更新Composer。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n注意\r\nDuring the installation of Yii, \r\nYii安装期间，\r\nComposer will need to request a lot of information from the Github API. \r\nComposer需要从Github API请求很多信息。\r\nThe number of requests depends on the number of dependencies your application has and may be bigger than the &lt;strong&gt;Github API rate limit&lt;/strong&gt;. \r\n请求的数量取决于您的应用程序所依赖的数量， 并可能大于 &lt;strong&gt;Github API 速率限制&lt;/strong&gt;。\r\nIf you hit this limit, Composer may ask for your Github login credentials to obtain a Github API access token. \r\n如果达到此限制，Composer 可能会要求您提供 Github 登录凭据以获取 Github API 访问令牌。\r\nOn fast connections you may hit this limit earlier than Composer can handle so we recommend to configure the access token before installing Yii. \r\n在快速连接上，您可能比 Composer 能够处理的时间早， 因此我们建议您在安装 Yii 之前配置访问令牌。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/articles/troubleshooting.md#api-rate-limit-and-oauth-tokens&quot;&gt;Composer documentation about Github API tokens&lt;/a&gt; for instructions on how to do this.\r\n有关如何执行此操作的说明，请参阅 &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/articles/troubleshooting.md#api-rate-limit-and-oauth-tokens&quot;&gt;Composer documentation about Github API tokens&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Installing Yii&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n安装Yii\r\nWith Composer installed, you can install Yii application template by running the following command under a Web-accessible folder:\r\n安装 Composer 后，您可以通过在 Web 可访问的文件夹下运行以下命令来安装Yii应用程序模板：\r\ncomposer create-project --prefer-dist yiisoft/yii2-app-basic basic\r\n\r\nThis will install the latest stable version of Yii application template in a directory named &lt;code&gt;basic&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n这将在名为basic的目录中安装最新稳定版本的Yii应用程序模板。\r\nYou can choose a different directory name if you want.\r\n如果需要，您可以选择不同的目录名称。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Info: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n信息\r\nIf the &lt;code&gt;composer create-project&lt;/code&gt; command fails you may also refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/articles/troubleshooting.md&quot;&gt;Troubleshooting section of the Composer Documentation&lt;/a&gt; for common errors. \r\n如果&lt;code&gt;composer create-project&lt;/code&gt; 命令失败了，你还可参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/articles/troubleshooting.md&quot;&gt;Troubleshooting section of the Composer Documentation&lt;/a&gt;以了解常见错误。\r\nWhen you have fixed the error, \r\n当你修复了错误，\r\nyou can resume the aborted installation by running &lt;code&gt;composer update&lt;/code&gt; inside of the &lt;code&gt;basic&lt;/code&gt; directory.\r\n您可以通过在 &lt;code&gt;basic&lt;/code&gt; 目录内运行 &lt;code&gt;composer update&lt;/code&gt; 来恢复中止安装。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Tip: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n提示：\r\nIf you want to install the latest development version of Yii, \r\n如果你想安装最新的Yii开发版本，\r\nyou may use the following command instead, \r\n可以使用以下添加一个stability选项命令代替，\r\nwhich adds a &lt;a href=&quot;https://getcomposer.org/doc/04-schema.md#minimum-stability&quot;&gt;stability option&lt;/a&gt;:\r\n它添加了一个stability选项：\r\ncomposer create-project --prefer-dist --stability=dev yiisoft/yii2-app-basic basic\r\n\r\nNote that the development version of Yii should not be used for production as it may break your running code.\r\n请注意，Yii的开发版本不应该用于生产，因为它可能会破坏您的运行代码。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Installing from an Archive File &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n从一个存档文件安装\r\nInstalling Yii from an archive file involves three steps:\r\n从存档文件安装Yii包括三个步骤：\r\nDownload the archive file from &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.yiiframework.com/download/&quot;&gt;yiiframework.com&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n从&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.yiiframework.com/download/&quot;&gt;yiiframework.com&lt;/a&gt; 下载存档文件。\r\nUnpack the downloaded file to a Web-accessible folder.\r\n将下载的文件解压到Web可访问的文件夹中。\r\nModify the &lt;code&gt;config/web.php&lt;/code&gt; file by entering a secret key for the &lt;code&gt;cookieValidationKey&lt;/code&gt; configuration item \r\n修改 &lt;code&gt;config/web.php&lt;/code&gt; 文件，给 &lt;code&gt;cookieValidationKey&lt;/code&gt; 配置项 添加一个密钥\r\n(this is done automatically if you are installing Yii using Composer):\r\n(若你通过 Composer 安装，则此步骤会自动完成)\r\n\r\n// !!! insert a secret key in the following (if it is empty) - this is required by cookie validation\r\n&amp;#39;cookieValidationKey&amp;#39; =&amp;gt; &amp;#39;enter your secret key here&amp;#39;,&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Other Installation Options&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n别的安装选择\r\nThe above installation instructions show how to install Yii,\r\n上面的安装说明显示了如何安装Yii，\r\nwhich also creates a basic Web application that works out of the box. \r\n它还创建了一个开箱即用的基本Web应用程序。\r\nThis approach is a good starting point for most projects, either small or big. \r\n这种方法是大多数项目的良好起点，无论是小项目还是大项目。\r\nIt is especially suitable if you just start learning Yii.\r\n如果你刚开始学Yii的话就特别合适了。\r\nBut there are other installation options available:\r\n但也有其他可用的安装选项：\r\nIf you only want to install the core framework and would like to build an entire application from scratch, \r\n如果您只想安装核心框架并从头开始构建整个应用程序，\r\nyou may follow the instructions as explained in &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-start-from-scratch&quot;&gt;Building Application from Scratch&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n您可以按照&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-start-from-scratch&quot;&gt;Building Application from Scratch&lt;/a&gt;中的说明进行操作。\r\nIf you want to start with a more sophisticated application, \r\n如果你想从更复杂的应用程序开始，\r\nbetter suited to team development environments, \r\n更适合团队开发环境，\r\nyou may consider installing the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-app-advanced/blob/master/docs/guide/README.md&quot;&gt;Advanced Project Template&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n你可以考虑安装&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-app-advanced/blob/master/docs/guide/README.md&quot;&gt;Advanced Project Template&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Installing Assets&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n安装Assets\r\nYii relies on &lt;a href=&quot;http://bower.io/&quot;&gt;Bower&lt;/a&gt; and/or &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npmjs.org/&quot;&gt;NPM&lt;/a&gt; packages for the asset (CSS and JavaScript) libraries installation. \r\nYii依靠 &lt;a href=&quot;http://bower.io/&quot;&gt;Bower&lt;/a&gt; 和/或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npmjs.org/&quot;&gt;NPM&lt;/a&gt; 软件包来安装 asset（CSS 和 JavaScript）库。\r\nIt uses Composer to obtain these libraries, \r\n它使用Composer来获取这些库，\r\nallowing PHP and CSS/JavaScript package versions to resolve at the same time. \r\n允许同时解析PHP和CSS/JavaScript包版本。\r\nThis can be achieved either by usage of &lt;a href=&quot;https://asset-packagist.org/&quot;&gt;asset-packagist.org&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/francoispluchino/composer-asset-plugin/&quot;&gt;composer asset plugin&lt;/a&gt;. \r\n这可以通过使用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://asset-packagist.org/&quot;&gt;asset-packagist.org&lt;/a&gt; 或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/francoispluchino/composer-asset-plugin/&quot;&gt;composer asset plugin&lt;/a&gt; 来实现。\r\nPlease refer to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-assets&quot;&gt;Assets documentation&lt;/a&gt; for more details.\r\n更多详细请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/structure-assets&quot;&gt;Assets documentation&lt;/a&gt;。\r\nYou may want to either manage your assets via native Bower/NPM client, \r\n您可能希望通过本地 Bower/NPM 客户端管理您的 assets，\r\nuse CDN or avoid assets installation entirely. \r\n使用 CDN 或避免完全 assets 的安装。\r\nIn order to prevent assets installation via Composer, \r\n为防止通过Composer安装assets，\r\nadd the following lines to your &amp;#39;composer.json&amp;#39;:\r\n添加下面几行到你的&amp;#39;composer.json&amp;#39;:\r\n&amp;quot;replace&amp;quot;: {\r\n    &amp;quot;bower-asset/jquery&amp;quot;: &amp;quot;&amp;gt;=1.11.0&amp;quot;,\r\n    &amp;quot;bower-asset/inputmask&amp;quot;: &amp;quot;&amp;gt;=3.2.0&amp;quot;,\r\n    &amp;quot;bower-asset/punycode&amp;quot;: &amp;quot;&amp;gt;=1.3.0&amp;quot;,\r\n    &amp;quot;bower-asset/yii2-pjax&amp;quot;: &amp;quot;&amp;gt;=2.0.0&amp;quot;\r\n},\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n注意\r\nin case of bypassing asset installation via Composer,\r\n如果绕过了通过Composer安装asset,\r\nyou are responsible for the assets installation and resolving version collisions. \r\n您负责 assets 的安装和解决版本冲突。\r\nBe prepared for possible inconsistencies among asset files from different extensions.\r\n为来自不同扩展名的assets文件之间可能出现的不一致做好准备。\r\n准备来自不同扩展名的 assets 文件之间的可能不一致。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Verifying the Installation&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n验证安装\r\nAfter installation is done, \r\n安装完成后，\r\neither configure your web server (see next section) \r\n配置你的web服务器（看下一段）\r\nor use the &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/features.commandline.webserver.php&quot;&gt;built-in PHP web server&lt;/a&gt; by running the following console command while in the project root directory:\r\n或者在项目根目录下运行以下控制台命令，使用内置的PHP web服务器：\r\nphp yii serve\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Note: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n注意\r\nBy default the HTTP-server will listen to port 8080. \r\n默认情况下HTTP服务器 将监听端口8080。\r\nHowever if that port is already in use or you wish to serve multiple applications this way, \r\n但是，如果该端口已在使用中，或者您希望以这种方式为多个应用程序提供服务，\r\nyou might want to specify what port to use. Just add the --port argument:\r\n您可能需要指定要使用的端口。只需添加--port参数：\r\nphp yii serve --port=8888\r\n\r\nYou can use your browser to access the installed Yii application with the following URL:\r\n您可以使用浏览器访问已安装的Yii应用程序，网址如下：\r\nhttp://localhost:8080/&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;You should see the above &amp;quot;Congratulations!&amp;quot; page in your browser. \r\n你应该可以在浏览器中看到如上所示的 &amp;ldquo;Congratulations!&amp;rdquo; 页面。\r\nIf not, please check if your PHP installation satisfies Yii&amp;#39;s requirements. \r\n如果没有，请检查您的PHP安装是否满足Yii的要求。\r\nYou can check if the minimum requirements are met using one of the following approaches:\r\n您可以使用以下方法之一检查是否满足最低要求：\r\nCopy &lt;code&gt;/requirements.php&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;/web/requirements.php&lt;/code&gt; and then use a browser to access it via\r\n &lt;code&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/requirements.php&quot;&gt;http://localhost/requirements.php&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/code&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Run the following commands:\r\n允许如下命令：\r\n\r\ncd basic\r\nphp requirements.php&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;You should configure your PHP installation so that it meets the minimum requirements of Yii. \r\n您应该配置PHP安装，使其满足Yii的最低要求。\r\nMost importantly, you should have PHP 5.4 or above. \r\n最重要的是，您应该拥有PHP 5.4或更高版本。\r\nIdeally latest PHP 7. You should also install the &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/manual/en/pdo.installation.php&quot;&gt;PDO PHP Extension&lt;/a&gt; and a corresponding database driver (such as &lt;code&gt;pdo_mysql&lt;/code&gt; for MySQL databases), if your application needs a database.\r\n最好是最新的PHP7。如果应用程序需要数据库，还应该安装PDO PHP扩展和相应的数据库驱动程序（如PDO_mysql for mysql数据库）。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Configuring Web Servers &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n配置web服务器\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Info: ﻿&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n信息\r\nYou may skip this subsection for now if you are just test driving Yii with no intention of deploying it to a production server.\r\n如果你现在只是要试用 Yii 而不是将其部署到生产环境中， 本小节可以跳过。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;The application installed according to the above instructions should work out of box with either an &lt;a href=&quot;http://httpd.apache.org/&quot;&gt;Apache HTTP server&lt;/a&gt; or an &lt;a href=&quot;http://nginx.org/&quot;&gt;Nginx HTTP server&lt;/a&gt;, on Windows, Mac OS X, or Linux running PHP 5.4 or higher. \r\n按照上述方法安装的应用程序在 Windows，Max OS X， Linux 中的 &lt;a href=&quot;http://httpd.apache.org/&quot;&gt;Apache HTTP 服务器&lt;/a&gt; 或 &lt;a href=&quot;http://nginx.org/&quot;&gt;Nginx HTTP 服务器&lt;/a&gt;且PHP版本为5.4或更高都可以直接运行。\r\nYii 2.0 is also compatible with facebook&amp;#39;s &lt;a href=&quot;http://hhvm.com/&quot;&gt;HHVM&lt;/a&gt;.\r\nYii 2.0 也兼容 Facebook 公司的 &lt;a href=&quot;http://hhvm.com/&quot;&gt;HHVM&lt;/a&gt;，\r\nHowever, there are some edge cases where HHVM behaves different than native PHP, \r\n但是， HHVM 和标准 PHP 在边界案例上有些地方略有不同，\r\nso you have to take some extra care when using HHVM.\r\n所以在使用HHVM时你必须格外小心。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;On a production server, \r\n在生产环境的服务器上，\r\nyou may want to configure your Web server so that the application can be accessed via the URL &lt;code&gt;http://www.example.com/index.php&lt;/code&gt; instead of &lt;code&gt;http://www.example.com/basic/web/index.php&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n您可能需要配置Web服务器，以便可以通过URL http://www.example.com/index.php而不是http://www.example.com/basic/Web/index.php访问应用程序。\r\nSuch configuration requires pointing the document root of your Web server to the &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; folder. \r\n这种配置需要将 Web 服务器的文档根目录(document root)指向 &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; 目录。\r\nYou may also want to hide &lt;code&gt;index.php&lt;/code&gt; from the URL, as described in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/runtime-routing&quot;&gt;Routing and URL Creation&lt;/a&gt; section. \r\n可能你还会想隐藏掉 URL 中的 &lt;code&gt;index.php&lt;/code&gt;，具体细节在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/zh-cn/runtime-url-handling&quot;&gt;URL 解析和生成&lt;/a&gt;一章中有介绍。\r\nIn this subsection, you&amp;#39;ll learn how to configure your Apache or Nginx server to achieve these goals.\r\n在本小节中，您将学习如何配置Apache或Nginx服务器来实现这些目标。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;info: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\nBy setting &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; as the document root,\r\n将 &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; 设置为文档根目录(document root)，\r\nyou also prevent end users from accessing your private application code and sensitive data files that are stored in the sibling directories of &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n您还防止终端用户访问存储在 &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; 的相邻目录中的私有应用代码和敏感数据文件。\r\nDenying access to those other folders is a security improvement.\r\n禁止对其他目录的访问是一个不错的安全改进。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Info: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n信息\r\nIf your application will run in a shared hosting environment where you do not have permission to modify its Web server configuration, \r\n如果您的应用程序将在您无权修改其Web服务器配置的共享宿主环境中运行，\r\nyou may still adjust the structure of your application for better security. \r\n您仍然可以调整应用程序的结构以提高安全性。\r\nPlease refer to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-shared-hosting&quot;&gt;Shared Hosting Environment&lt;/a&gt; section for more details.\r\n更多细节请参考&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-shared-hosting&quot;&gt;Shared Hosting Environment&lt;/a&gt; 章节。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Info:﻿&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n信息\r\nIf you are running your Yii application behind a reverse proxy,\r\n如果您在反向代理后面运行Yii应用程序，\r\nyou might need to configure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/runtime-requests#trusted-proxies&quot;&gt;Trusted proxies and headers&lt;/a&gt; in the request component.\r\n则可能需要在请求组件中配置 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/zh-cn/runtime-requests#trusted-proxies&quot;&gt;Trusted proxies and headers&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Recommended Apache Configuration&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n建议的Apache配置\r\nUse the following configuration in Apache&amp;#39;s &lt;code&gt;httpd.conf&lt;/code&gt; file or within a virtual host configuration. \r\n在 Apache 的 &lt;code&gt;httpd.conf&lt;/code&gt; 文件或在一个虚拟主机配置文件中使用如下配置。\r\nNote that you should replace &lt;code&gt;path/to/basic/web&lt;/code&gt; with the actual path for &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt;.\r\n注意，你应该用&lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt;的实际路径替换&lt;code&gt;path/to/basic/web。&lt;/code&gt;\r\n&lt;code&gt;# Set document root to be &amp;quot;basic/web&amp;quot;\r\nDocumentRoot &amp;quot;path/to/basic/web&amp;quot;\r\n\r\n&amp;lt;Directory &amp;quot;path/to/basic/web&amp;quot;&amp;gt;\r\n    # use mod_rewrite for pretty URL support\r\n    RewriteEngine on\r\n    \r\n    # if $showScriptName is false in UrlManager, do not allow accessing URLs with script name\r\n    RewriteRule ^index.php/ - [L,R=404]\r\n    \r\n    # If a directory or a file exists, use the request directly\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\n    \r\n    # Otherwise forward the request to index.php\r\n    RewriteRule . index.php\r\n\r\n    # ...other settings...\r\n&amp;lt;/Directory&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Recommended Nginx Configuration&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n建议的Nginx配置\r\nTo use &lt;a href=&quot;http://wiki.nginx.org/&quot;&gt;Nginx&lt;/a&gt;, \r\n要用Nginx,\r\nyou should install PHP as an &lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/install.fpm&quot;&gt;FPM SAPI&lt;/a&gt;. \r\n您应该将PHP安装为&lt;a href=&quot;https://secure.php.net/install.fpm&quot;&gt;FPM SAPI&lt;/a&gt;。\r\nYou may use the following Nginx configuration, \r\n你可以使用如下的Nginx配置，\r\nreplacing &lt;code&gt;path/to/basic/web&lt;/code&gt; with the actual path for &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;mysite.test&lt;/code&gt; with the actual hostname to serve.\r\n将 &lt;code&gt;path/to/basic/web&lt;/code&gt; 替换为实际的 &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; 目录， &lt;code&gt;mysite.local&lt;/code&gt; 替换为实际的主机名以提供服务。\r\nserver {\r\n    charset utf-8;\r\n    client_max_body_size 128M;\r\n\r\n    listen 80; ## listen for ipv4\r\n    #listen [::]:80 default_server ipv6only=on; ## listen for ipv6\r\n\r\n    server_name mysite.test;\r\n    root        /path/to/basic/web;\r\n    index       index.php;\r\n\r\n    access_log  /path/to/basic/log/access.log;\r\n    error_log   /path/to/basic/log/error.log;\r\n\r\n    location / {\r\n        # Redirect everything that isn&amp;#39;t a real file to index.php\r\n        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.php$is_args$args;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    # uncomment to avoid processing of calls to non-existing static files by Yii\r\n    #location ~ \\.(js|css|png|jpg|gif|swf|ico|pdf|mov|fla|zip|rar)$ {\r\n    #    try_files $uri =404;\r\n    #}\r\n    #error_page 404 /404.html;\r\n\r\n    # deny accessing php files for the /assets directory\r\n    location ~ ^/assets/.*\\.php$ {\r\n        deny all;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    location ~ \\.php$ {\r\n        include fastcgi_params;\r\n        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\r\n        fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;\r\n        #fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php5-fpm.sock;\r\n        try_files $uri =404;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    location ~* /\\. {\r\n        deny all;\r\n    }\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;When using this configuration, \r\n当使用这个配置时，\r\nyou should also set &lt;code&gt;cgi.fix_pathinfo=0&lt;/code&gt; in the &lt;code&gt;php.ini&lt;/code&gt; file in order to avoid many unnecessary system &lt;code&gt;stat()&lt;/code&gt; calls.\r\n你还应该在 &lt;code&gt;php.ini&lt;/code&gt; 文件中设置 &lt;code&gt;cgi.fix_pathinfo=0&lt;/code&gt; ， 能避免掉很多不必要的 &lt;code&gt;stat()&lt;/code&gt; 系统调用。\r\n\r\n\r\nAlso note that when running an HTTPS server, \r\n还要注意当正在运行一个HTTPS服务时，\r\nyou need to add &lt;code&gt;fastcgi_param HTTPS on;&lt;/code&gt; \r\n你需要添加&lt;code&gt;fastcgi_param HTTPS on&lt;/code&gt;\r\nso that Yii can properly detect if a connection is secure.\r\n这样 Yii 才能正确地判断连接是否安全。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;IIS Configuration&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nIt&amp;#39;s recommended to host the application in a virtual host where document root points to &lt;code&gt;path/to/app/web&lt;/code&gt; folder. \r\n建议将应用程序托管在一个虚拟主机中，其中文档根目录指向path/to/app/web文件夹。\r\nIn that &lt;code&gt;web&lt;/code&gt; folder you have to place a file named &lt;code&gt;web.config&lt;/code&gt; i.e. &lt;code&gt;path/to/app/web/web.config&lt;/code&gt;. \r\n在该web文件夹中，您必须放置一个名为web.config的文件，即path/to/app/web/web.config。\r\nweb目录中必须有一个文件名叫&lt;code&gt;web.config&lt;/code&gt;即：&lt;code&gt;path/to/app/web/web.config&lt;/code&gt;。\r\nContent of the file should be the following:\r\n文件的内容应如下：\r\n&amp;lt;?xml version=&amp;quot;1.0&amp;quot; encoding=&amp;quot;UTF-8&amp;quot;?&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;lt;system.webServer&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;lt;directoryBrowse enabled=&amp;quot;false&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;\r\n  &amp;lt;rewrite&amp;gt;\r\n    &amp;lt;rules&amp;gt;\r\n      &amp;lt;rule name=&amp;quot;Hide Yii Index&amp;quot; stopProcessing=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot;&amp;gt;\r\n        &amp;lt;match url=&amp;quot;.&amp;quot; ignoreCase=&amp;quot;false&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;\r\n        &amp;lt;conditions&amp;gt;\r\n        &amp;lt;add input=&amp;quot;{REQUEST_FILENAME}&amp;quot; matchType=&amp;quot;IsFile&amp;quot; \r\n              ignoreCase=&amp;quot;false&amp;quot; negate=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;\r\n        &amp;lt;add input=&amp;quot;{REQUEST_FILENAME}&amp;quot; matchType=&amp;quot;IsDirectory&amp;quot; \r\n              ignoreCase=&amp;quot;false&amp;quot; negate=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;\r\n        &amp;lt;/conditions&amp;gt;\r\n        &amp;lt;action type=&amp;quot;Rewrite&amp;quot; url=&amp;quot;index.php&amp;quot; appendQueryString=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;\r\n      &amp;lt;/rule&amp;gt; \r\n    &amp;lt;/rules&amp;gt;\r\n  &amp;lt;/rewrite&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;lt;/system.webServer&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Running Applications&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n运行应用\r\nAfter installing Yii, \r\n安装Yii后,\r\nyou have a working Yii application that can be accessed via the URL &lt;code&gt;http://hostname/basic/web/index.php&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;http://hostname/index.php&lt;/code&gt;, depending upon your configuration. \r\n您有一个工作的Yii应用程序，可以通过URL http://hostname/basic/web/index.php或http://hostname/index.php访问，具体取决于您的配置。\r\nThis section will introduce the application&amp;#39;s built-in functionality, \r\n本节将介绍应用程序的内置功能，\r\nhow the code is organized, and how the application handles requests in general.\r\n代码的组织方式，以及应用程序通常如何处理请求。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Info: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\nFor simplicity, \r\n为了简单起见，\r\nthroughout this &amp;quot;Getting Started&amp;quot; tutorial, \r\n在本&amp;ldquo;入门&amp;rdquo;教程中，\r\nit&amp;#39;s assumed that you have set &lt;code&gt;basic/web&lt;/code&gt; as the document root of your Web server, \r\n假设您已经将basic/web设置为web服务器的文档根目录，\r\nand configured the URL for accessing your application to be &lt;code&gt;http://hostname/index.php&lt;/code&gt; or something similar. \r\n并将访问应用程序的URL配置为http://hostname/index.php或类似的内容。\r\nFor your needs, please adjust the URLs in our descriptions accordingly.\r\n根据您的需要，请相应地调整我们描述中的url。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;Note that unlike framework itself, \r\n注意，不同与框架本身，\r\nafter project template is installed it&amp;#39;s all yours. \r\n安装项目模板后，一切都归你了。\r\nYou&amp;#39;re free to add or delete code and overall modify it as you need.\r\n您可以自由添加或删除代码，并根据需要对其进行总体修改。&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Functionality&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n功能\r\nThe basic application installed contains four pages:\r\n安装的基本应用程序包含四个页面：\r\nthe homepage, displayed when you access the URL &lt;code&gt;http://hostname/index.php&lt;/code&gt;,\r\n主页，当您访问URL&lt;code&gt;http://hostname/index.php&lt;/code&gt;时显示，\r\nthe &amp;quot;About&amp;quot; page,\r\nAbout页面，\r\nthe &amp;quot;Contact&amp;quot; page, which displays a Contact form that allows end users to contact you via email,\r\n&amp;ldquo;Contact&amp;rdquo;页面，显示允许终端用户通过电子邮件与您联系的联系人表单，\r\nand the &amp;quot;Login&amp;quot; page, which displays a login form that can be used to authenticate end users. \r\n以及&amp;ldquo;登录&amp;rdquo;页面，其中显示可用于验证终端用户身份的登录表单。\r\nTry logging in with &amp;quot;admin/admin&amp;quot;, and you will find the &amp;quot;Login&amp;quot; main menu item will change to &amp;quot;Logout&amp;quot;.\r\n试着用&amp;quot;admin/admin&amp;quot;登录，你会发现主菜单项&amp;quot;Login&amp;quot;被更改为&amp;quot;Logout&amp;quot;。\r\nThese pages share a common header and footer. \r\n这些页面共享一个公共的header和footer。\r\nThe header contains a main menu bar to allow navigation among different pages.\r\nheader包含了一个可以在不同页面间切换的导航栏。\r\nYou should also see a toolbar at the bottom of the browser window. \r\n您还应该在浏览器窗口的底部看到一个工具栏。\r\nThis is a useful &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-debug/blob/master/docs/guide/README.md&quot;&gt;debugger tool&lt;/a&gt; provided by Yii to record and display a lot of debugging information, \r\n这个Yii提供的一个有用的调试工具，可以记录和显示大量的调试信息，\r\nsuch as log messages, response statuses, the database queries run, and so on.\r\n如：日志信息，响应状态，数据库查询运行等等。\r\nAdditionally to the web application, there is a console script called &lt;code&gt;yii&lt;/code&gt;, which is located in the applications base directory. \r\n除了web应用程序之外，还有一个名为yii的控制台脚本，它位于应用程序根目录。\r\nThis script can be used to run background and maintenance tasks for the application, which are described in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-console&quot;&gt;Console Application Section&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n此脚本可用于运行应用程序的后台和维护任务，如&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/guide/2.0/en/tutorial-console&quot;&gt;Console Application&lt;/a&gt;部分所述。\r\n\r\n&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre aria-autocomplete=&quot;list&quot; aria-expanded=&quot;false&quot; aria-label=&quot;Write…&quot; aria-multiline=&quot;true&quot; contenteditable=&quot;true&quot; data-is-placeholder-visible=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Application Structure&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n应用结构\r\nThe most important directories and files in your application are (assuming the application&amp;#39;s root directory is &lt;code&gt;basic&lt;/code&gt;):\r\n应用程序中最重要的目录和文件是（假设应用程序的根目录是basic）：\r\nbasic/                  应用程序根目录\r\n    composer.json       由Composer使用，描述包信息\r\n    config/             包含应用配置和其它配置\r\n        console.php     控制台应用配置\r\n        web.php         web应用配置\r\n    commands/           包含控制台命令类\r\n    controllers/        contains controller classes\r\n    models/             contains model classes\r\n    runtime/            contains files generated by Yii during runtime, such as logs and cache files\r\n    vendor/             contains the installed Composer packages, including the Yii framework itself\r\n    views/              contains view files\r\n    web/                application Web root, contains Web accessible files\r\n        assets/         contains published asset files (javascript and css) by Yii\r\n        index.php       the entry (or bootstrap) script for the application\r\n    yii                 the Yii console command execution script&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Powered by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1&quot; title=&quot;Froala Editor&quot;&gt;Froala Editor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','2018-03-28 16:05:08','2020-02-28 19:19:06','1'),
	(731,1,81,'docker启动后自动退出','&lt;h3&gt;退出原因&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;1、docker容器运行必须有一个前台进程， 如果没有前台进程执行，容器认为空闲，就会自行退出&lt;br&gt;2、容器运行的命令如果不是那些一直挂起的命令（ 运行top，tail、循环等），就是会自动退出&lt;br&gt;3、这个是 docker 的机制问题&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Powered by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1&quot; title=&quot;Froala Editor&quot;&gt;Froala Editor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Powered by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1&quot; title=&quot;Froala Editor&quot;&gt;Froala Editor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','2018-03-28 16:05:08','2020-02-10 13:20:49','1'),
	(732,1,18,'ecshop-v4.0','&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;files structure:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;/admin/includes/init.php &lt;em&gt;管理中心公用文件 -&amp;gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;/includes/cls_ecshop.php 基础类&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后台登录&amp;nbsp;/admin/privilege.php -&amp;gt;/admin/includes/init.php&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;/admin/includes/init.php&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;//str_replace(&amp;#39;\\\\&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;/&amp;#39;, dirname(__FILE__)) 这个是针对window 环境下防止输出的时候，目录分隔符号不一样\r\n//下面这行意思是如果是window 环境就把 \\ 替换成 /，然后把 /path/ecshop/code/source/ecshop/admin/includes 替换为 /path/ecshop/code/source/ecshop/includes\r\nrequire_once(str_replace(&amp;#39;/admin/includes&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;/includes&amp;#39;,str_replace(&amp;#39;\\\\&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;/&amp;#39;, dirname(__FILE__))) . &amp;#39;/safety.php&amp;#39;);&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;/* 初始化设置 */\r\n@ini_set(&amp;#39;memory_limit&amp;#39;,          &amp;#39;64M&amp;#39;);\r\n@ini_set(&amp;#39;session.cache_expire&amp;#39;,  600);\r\n@ini_set(&amp;#39;session.use_trans_sid&amp;#39;, 0);\r\n@ini_set(&amp;#39;session.use_cookies&amp;#39;,   1);\r\n@ini_set(&amp;#39;session.auto_start&amp;#39;,    0);\r\n@ini_set(&amp;#39;display_errors&amp;#39;,        0);&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pb